(3085, 'en_US', 'Fallabella', 'For a taste of traditional Italian with a touch of Mediterranean flavor', 'Pene della casa, Mix tapas Platter, Wild rocket salad', '', 'Recognized as “One of the Top Ten Italian Restaurants” in Bangkok by the Italian Embassy. The Italian dishes are elaborately prepared in an authentic and traditional Italian food at its best. The ambience of the restaurant is superior and the staff provide the attentive service.', 'Next to the BTS skytrain station and is conveniently close to many five stars hotels and shopping centres such as Four Seasons, Grand Hyatt Erawan, Central World and Siam Paragon.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3086, 'en_US', 'Bacco–Osteria da Sergio', 'The most popular and best quality in town by Bangkok Post.', 'Ravioli crema di tartufo, Fiore salad, Lamb chop', '', 'Bacco has been recommened by none other than Thailand Tatler to be a top eatery in Bangkok.The Bangkok Post has announced this establishment to be the most popular and best quality in town. The ambience of the restaurant is cozy atmosphere and the staff provide the attentive service.', '10 minutes by walk from BTS Thong Lo', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3087, 'en_US', 'Koi Restaurant & Lounge Bar', 'Fantastic food with flawless service.', 'Miso Bronzed Black Cod Medley of Vegetable, Creamy Rock  Shrimp Tempura, Salmon Salad', '', 'Koi Restaurants are well known globally amongst Leading Business Men, Hollywood Movie Stars and Hi-end Celebrities for their Contemporary Japanese Cuisine with Califonian twist, impeccable facilities, service and unique ambience.', 'From BTS Asoke and take a taxi go to sukhumvit road soi Sainamphueng around 25 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3088, 'en_US', 'Ten Sui', 'This is the place for real traditional Japanese food.', 'Kaiseki course, Hot stone grilled matsuzaka beef, Omakase sushi', '', 'Ten Sui is where you can sit by a window overlooking a little Zen garden and be treated to true Japanese hospitality by an owner who is the soul of kindness and intelligence. The ambience of the restaurant is superior and the staff provide the attentive service.', 'BTS Asoke, MRT Sukhumvit', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3089, 'en_US', 'Le Vendome', 'A wonderful experience with a great cuisine.', 'Terrine of foie gras, Rack of lamb, Apple tart', '', 'Experience premium-quality U.S Black Angus, Australian, and Japanese Kagoshima Beef and featured in a variety of delicious dishes. Don’t miss out on the world’s best beef. The ambience of the restaurant is superior and the staff provide the attentive service.', 'BTS Phrom Phong and then take a taxi to Sukhumvit soi 31 around 10 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3090, 'en_US', 'Zucca Wine Bar & Restaurant', 'The best Spaghetti and Risotto Nero in Bangkok.', 'Risotto Nero', '', 'A hidden gem in Sukhumvit. It\'s not conspicuous, but it\'s well worth seeking out because of the high quality of food and elegant presentation.The ambience of the restaurant is superior and the staff provide the attentive service with friend welcome.', '5 minutes walk from BTS Asoke.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3091, 'en_US', 'The Myth of Mahanaga', 'Experience delicious, creative Thai cuisine in our beautiful ambience', 'Slow-cooked pork belly with sauteed morning glory, Tom yum kung with fried crispy prawns, Sous vide massaman kai with risotto and crispy sweet lotus', '', 'Mahanaga Restaurant & Bar serves modern Thai cuisine. Offering the very best of Thai hospitality in an outstandingly designed atmosphere featuring two dining pavillions, an indoor bar and outdoor courtyard.', 'BTS Phrom Phong and take a taxi go to soi Sukhumvit 29 around 10 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3092, 'en_US', 'Water Library Chamchuri', 'Best fine dining in Bangkok to die for.', 'Crete brûlée', '', 'Water Library Chamchuri turns into an exclusive fine dining experience at night. Whilst offering exceptional cuisine, tableside service paired with an extensive wine list.', 'MRT Samyan and take a taxi around 20 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3093, 'en_US', 'La Bottega di Luca', 'Another great Italian cuisine in Bangkok.', 'Angel hair with Canadian lobster, Mussel in white wine, Florentina tomahawk steak', '', 'The food is always good and well prepared. Staff are very welcoming, attentive and professional. The atmosphere on the terrace, no matter day or night is one of the best in Bangkok.', 'BTS Phrom Phong and take a taxi into Soi Sukhumvit 49 around 25 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3094, 'en_US', 'Vino di Zanotti (Bangkok)', 'Vino Di Zanotti , Best Italian food in the lovvely house', 'Australian Lamb, French lobster with angel hair, Zanotti pizza', '', 'VINO di Zanotti embraces the concept of the Italian Aperitivo, providing a meeting place for professionals to wind down after work and enjoy quality wines and food in a sophisticated  and relaxed ambience. Vino di Zanotti has a great atmosphere, with excellent food in Bangkok.', 'MRT Klongtoey and take a taxi to Nanglinchy road around 30 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3095, 'en_US', 'Harvey', 'The inspried Californai cuisine.', 'Steak tartar, Carpaccio, Oxtail stew', '', 'This is a perfect place to dining, especially for a special occasion, because of the posh atmosphere and delicious food. Fresh ingridients, convient parking space, and best wine from all over the world.', 'BTS Thong Lo and take a taxi to soi Thong Lo 9 around 20 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3096, 'en_US', 'My Collection', 'A nice restaurant with a great atmosphere.', 'River Prawn + Bacon Spaghetti and Green Salad, Beef Carpacio', '', 'My Collection offers the most romantic and intoxicating place to be in Bangkok. Not to mention this restaurant has been often called \"the perfect aphrodisiac\". Enjoy the best food in the best atmosphere', 'BTS Ploenchit and take a taxi go inside Wireless around 20 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3097, 'en_US', 'Maru Kaiseki Japanese Restaurant', 'A very good value of food in Bangkok.', 'Salad tofu, Soup fish, Yakisoba, Sashimi', '', 'Maru Kaiseki is a Japnaese restaurant that serves the premium indredients importing from Japan. Highlight is the vast selection of Premium grade Sashimi as well as the rare choices of fish. This place is the real heaven for Sashimi lover.', 'BTS Thong Lo and taxe a taxi to go inside soi Thong Lo 3 aound 15  minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3098, 'en_US', 'Zanotti IL Ristorante Italiano', 'The kind of Italian food that you won\'t forget.', 'Tiramisu, Deep Fried Soft-Shell Crab Salad, Pama Pizza', '', 'Probably one of the best Italian restaurants in Asia Pacific Area, founded in 1998 by Chef Gianmaria Zanotti. The emphasis is on fresh ingredients and recipes from Northern Italy.', 'BTS Saladange and take a taxi to soi Saladang around 15 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3100, 'en_US', 'Bangkok Bitter, The Bar & The Restaurant', 'Great value of beer & pizza in Bangkok.', 'Bangkok bitter special, Pasta Cabonara, caramari flitti, Black Pizza', '', 'Tasty Food, especially the signature (black) pizza is nice. Staff is very friendly, helpful and calm. There is a small live band making soft background music, not loud but very nice.You difinitely have to be back....', 'BTS Thong Lo and take a taxi to soi Thong lor 5 around 20 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3101, 'en_US', 'ARTUR Restaurant', 'A very nice restaurant for fine dining in Bangkok.', 'Rack of lamb, Côte De Beouf, Pan Seared Foie Gras', '', 'Arthur is a phototype of western restaurant that bring you the best service. All of  staffs are determined to make you feel welcomed and happy. The service is as same as 5 stars hotel. Including with the tasty dishes, this is the reason why you can\'t miss Arthur. Don\'t forget to stop by to enjoy Arthur\'s cut!', 'BTS Chit Lom Station 200 meters', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3102, 'en_US', 'Tete Quarters by the River', 'Incredible and spectacular restaurant.', 'Ruby Soft Shell Crab Salad, BarBQ pork', '', 'Tete Quarters has the best service and food. With the breathe-taking riverview. It is a perfect place for those who want to have a special dinner at a special place. You can enjoy the best food and nice devoration.', 'BTS Sapantaksin and take a taxi to River city shopping center around 40 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3103, 'en_US', 'Paris Bangkok Restaurant', 'Steak and seafood with a French touch.', 'Fresh oyster, Onion soup', '', 'Paris Bangkok Restaurant is truely delicated to provide you with an amazing dining experience, no wonder it is benamed\" one of the best restaurant in Bangkok. It is the best combination between Thai and French.', 'BTS Saladange and walk inside Saladange soi 1 around 20 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3104, 'en_US', 'Amici by Pomodoro', 'Treat yourself if you are shopping \nat Siam Paragon mall.', 'Grilled rock lobster with rocket leaves, balsamic dressing, Spaghetti with prawns in pesto sauce, Oven baked snow fish with crispy polenta crust, Pizza Salmon, Baked chocolate stuffed with molten-chocolate, served with vanilla ice cream', '', 'In Amici by Pomodoro, you will enjoy good italian food served by friendly staff. The best Italian place that make you feel like eating food in Italy. Come and enjoy! You don\'t wanna miss this chance.', 'BTS Siam walk to Siam Paragon G floor', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3105, 'en_US', 'Karatama Robatayaki', 'Impressive, athentic and delicious.', 'Tapanyaki', '', 'The food is great as well as service. At Karatama Robatayaki, you will enjoy live cooking and a great taste of food. As a plus, all staff will do the special thank you to the guest after the meal.', 'BTS Asoke and take a taxi to soi Sukhumvit 49 around 25 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3106, 'en_US', 'GAGGAN', 'An explosion of all the sences not just a meal, but also a work of art on a plate.', 'Papdi chaat, Tasting menu, Tandoori lamb chops', '', 'Experience and discover the true meaning of progessive Indian with the constantly evovling tasting menu. Food and atmosphere of South Asia will make your life more interesting. Come and enjoy your life one of the best restaurants in Asia.', 'In Soi Langsuan Road', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3108, 'en_US', 'Supanniga Eating Room', 'Fine Thai food, simple and uncomplicate.', 'Moo cha muang, Nam prik khai pu, Yam nue lai', '', 'Supanniga Eating Room has the perfect combination of their passion in various cuisines and well intention to re-introduce the long lost recipes. The ones that were passed down from one generation to another.', 'From BTS Thong Lo take a taxi to go inside soi Thong Lo around 15 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3109, 'en_US', 'Snapper', 'A little slice of New Zealand.', 'Premium New Zealand seafood platter, New Zealand lamb chops, New Zealand fish and chips', '', 'Snapper is not just a restaurant; it is a glimpse of a nation’s obsession. You will enjoy a wild range of yummy seafood and meat dishes accompained with tasty New Zealand wines to wash it all down.', 'BTS Nana and take a taxi to Sukhumvit 11 around 20 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3110, 'en_US', 'Surface', 'Good mix of food, plus a nice experience.', 'Lamb rack with herb sauce, Escargot and bone marrow, Angel hair with hijiki', '', 'Looking for the ‘out-of-the-box’ and unexpected experience in the middle of Bangkok? Simply make your reservation at Surface Restaurant at Sukhumvit Soi 53.', 'BTS Thong Lo and Take a taxi go inside soi Thong Lo around 20 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3111, 'en_US', 'Shuffle', 'Absolutely the best burger in Bangkok.', 'Pork chop, One good burger, Shuffle steak', '', 'Small but deliciously executed menu, the staffs are well trained with great service. Shuffle serves great steak and salad and many more to choose.', 'Close to BTS Thong Lor', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3112, 'en_US', 'Quince', 'Quince is the right balance.', 'Organic roast chicken, Beetroot, blueberry, feta cheese and micro greens, Pork belly, fennel, apple slaw, red pepper jam', '', 'Quince is obsessed with quality and flavors, so they go out of their way to source the finest seasonal ingredients from suppliers who treat their produce and animals with care.', 'BTS Promtpong and take taxi to Sukhumvit 45 around 25 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3113, 'en_US', 'The Oyster Bar', 'Worth a visit for any seafod lovers.', 'Shellfish platter, Wild salmon, Oysters', '', 'The Oyster Bar is a great find in Bangkok. This beautiful modern restaurant is on the same scale as to those popular ones in San Francisco and Los Angeles, because the team truely understands oysters and seafood.', 'BTS Chong non tree and Take a taxi around 35 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3114, 'en_US', 'Philippe', 'Lovely great bistro with great price.', 'Pan-fried duck liver, Ravioli duck liver pasta, Pan-fried snow fish serano ham sauce', '', 'The menu is designed to highlight the freshest of products, and to skillfully bring out the natural taste of the food. Classic country dishes and slow-cooked casseroles are the most popular.', '5 minutes walk from BTS Promtpomg', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3115, 'en_US', 'Le Petit Zinc', 'Modern French cuisine in quiet neightberhood.', 'Rolled duck breast with foie gras, Lamb rack with ratatouille and roasted potatoes, Crepe with scallop, asparagus, tomato, white wine and lime sauce', '', 'Le Petit Zinc Yen Akart is a French restaurant offering bistro food and salted or sweet crepes, which are a specialty from Britanny in the North-West coast of France. The ambience of the restaurant is superior and the staff provide the attentive service.', 'On Yen Akart, near soi 1, in front of Mama Dolorès', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3116, 'en_US', 'Patara', 'Ultimate Thai experience in Thailand.', 'Slow-braised beef in coconut and mint sauce, Grilled Thai aubergine and crabmeat salad, Tamarind-glazed crispy fried duck confit', '', 'Patara is a perfect place to experience contemporary Thai food in a stylish and tranquil setting. Private rooms are available for corporate and family entertaining guests.', 'BTS Thong Lo and taxi taxi to soi Thong Lo 19 around 15 minutes', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3117, 'en_US', 'Paste', 'Classically inspired-creative Thai food.', 'Master stock poached pork neck with avocado and red grapefruit, Slow-braised Australian beef ribs with ginger, young tamarind leaves and mushroom soy, Beef cheek in hung lay curry', '', 'The guiding food philosophy at Paste is to maintain a compact and focused menu that strives for quality. The ambience of the restaurant is superior and the staff provide the attentive service and friendly welcome.', 'BTS Station Thong Lo', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3118, 'en_US', 'Oskar Bistro', 'More than a bistro. It\'s a space for a bite to eat, to greet and wine to drink.', 'Oskar salad, Pizza casablanca, Duck parmentier', '', 'Oskar is a space for a bite to eat, friends to greet and wine to drink. Known for value-for-money wines, consistently friendly service and hearty, delicious food. The menu is a selection of high quality ingredient and the ambience is very nice.', 'BTS Nana and Take a taxi around 15 minutes to soi Sukhumvit 11', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
