(4300, 'en_US', 'Cavalli Kitchen & Bar', 'Modern European restaurant led by Chef Aue', 'Black ink spaghetti with salmon, Spaghetti with Thai-styled sausages, Sticky rice risotto', '', 'Cavalli Kitchen & Bar is a Modern European restaurant led by Chef Aue who spent over 10 years polishing his cooking skill in New York and 5-star hotel in Bangkok. His food philosophy is to use as much local ingredients as possible while still maintaining European taste and technique.', '5 minutes drive from BTS Thong Lo Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
