(2919, 'en_US', 'Nami Teppanyaki Steakhouse - JW Marriott Hotel Bangkok', 'An outstanding place for Japanese teppanyaki.', 'Kobe beef striploin, Phuket lobster, Australian wagyu striploin', '', 'Nami Teppanyaki Bar is a creative Japanese steakhouse in Bangkok serving mouthwatering dishes made on an iron griddle right before your eyes with skilled chefs .', 'Take a 5 mins walk from BTS Ploenchit Station Exit4', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2920, 'en_US', 'Maya Restaurant and Bar - Holiday Inn Bangkok Sukhumvit', 'An authentic Indian restaurant with great city views.', 'Nally rogan josh, Sarson salmon tikka, Gulab jamun cheesecake', '', 'Maya authentic inspired Indian is a stylish Indian restaurant located on the 29th Floor. Perfect for business launches or romantic dinners. The adjacent bar offers sky high entertainment until 1 a.m.', 'Take a 5 mins walk from BTS Phrom Phong Station or MRT Sukhumvit Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2921, 'en_US', 'Lord Jim\'s - Mandarin Oriental Bangkok', 'Lord Jim serves the most popular wide selection of seafood&international dishes.', 'Iced seafood tower, Sea bass in rock salt, Lobster bisque', '', 'Lord Jim’s reputation for magnificent seafood is almost as well known as its namesake. Enjoying an uninterrupted view of the river. Focusing on the freshest seafood available, Lord Jim’s is particularly renowned for its sushi and sashimi dishes.', 'Take BTS to Saphan Taksin Station, go towards the Hotel Boat Pier and board the Mandarin Oriental shuttle boat.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2922, 'en_US', 'The China House - Mandarin Oriental Bangkok', 'Art Deco style, contemporary Cantonese flavours.', 'Oven roasted ‘Peking’ duck, Black pepper beef tenderloin, Wasabi prawns', '', 'The China House enjoys an opulent old-world feel with dark wood furnishings and atmospheric low lighting. Under talented Executive Chef Andy Leong Siew Fye, The China House features an a la carte menu.', 'Take BTS to Saphan Taksin Station, go towards the Hotel Boat Pier and board the Mandarin Oriental shuttle boat.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2923, 'en_US', 'Nahm - Metropolitan Bangkok Hotel', 'Nahm delivers the sophisticated spicing of  Thai delicacies from award-winning chef', 'Chiang Mai chicken curry, Kaffir lime relish with sweet pork, Durian with sticky rice', '', 'Nahm is a place both for serious gourmets and for those who desire to learn more about authentic local cuisine. Most of menus are authentic ancient food which are hard to see in other places.', 'Take a 10 mins taxi from BTS station, Chong Nonsi', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2924, 'en_US', 'Elements \n  - Okura Prestige Hotel', 'Elements, well executed modern gourmet cuisine in a beautifully crafted setting.', 'Alaskan cod fish, Foie Gras on Lime, Jack Creek Black Angus perfumed', '', 'International cuisine with menus that reflect a remarkable blend of textures, temperatures, flavours and colours. Enjoy stunning views of downtown Bangkok before dining in comfort and style in our culinary theatre complete with open kitchen.', 'Located next to BTS Ploenchit', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2925, 'en_US', 'Sra Bua by Kiin Kiin - Siam Kempinski Hotel', 'Thai-inspired cuisine with a modern twist.', 'Frozen red curry with lobster salad, Cod in green curry with salty beetroot and jasmine, Quail in aromatic coconut milk with sauteed mushroom', '', 'Sra Bua by Kiin Kiin offers a modern interpretation of Thai cuisine. As for dress code, Sra Bua by Kiin Kiin kindly ask our guests to refrain from wearing shorts, sleeveless T-Shirt, slippers and sandals.', 'Hotel’s golf cart service is available 24/7 to transport guests from BTS Siam station and vice versa.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2926, 'en_US', 'Scarlett Wine Bar & Restaurant - Pullman Bangkok Hotel G', 'Scarlett boasts a fine selection of wines along with tapas, daily specials.', 'Lobster and foie gras ravioli, cep mushroom cream, Saint-Jacques d’Hokkaido, Alaskan king crab salad, Chocolate mousse', '', 'Scarlett Wine Bar & Restaurant, located on the 37th floor is the latest meeting point for young executives who like to have fun and chill out. Scarlett boasts a fine selection of wines along with tapas, daily specials, imported cold cuts and showcasing a large variety of cheeses.', '7 mins walk from BTS Chong Nonsi station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2927, 'en_US', 'Mistral Restaurant - Pullman Bangkok Hotel G', 'A contemporary all day dining restaurant.', 'Dessert, Seafood, Sashimi', '', 'A contemporary all day dining restaurant located on the 2nd floor featuring gourmet selection of Asian and Western cuisines overlooked by French Executive Chef LAURENT VOGEL.', '7 mins walk from BTS Chong Nonsi station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2928, 'en_US', 'da Vinci Restaurant - Rembrandt Hotel Bangkok', 'A \"must dine\" experience for purveyors of fine Italian food and wines.', 'Chicken Risotto, Minestone Soup, Artichokes with Foie-Gras', '', 'Da Vinci\'s exquisite cuisine is accompanied by an enviable wine list.  A \"must dine\" experience for purveyors of fine Italian food and wines. The restaurant emphasizes on the classic taste and homely atmosphere.', '10 mins walk from BTS Asoke station and MRT Sukhumvit station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2929, 'en_US', 'Biscotti - Four Seasons Hotel', 'Biscotti is a fun, contemporary Italian restaurant in Bangkok.', 'Classic focaccia mascarpone with truffle oil, Black summer truffle risotto, prosecco, salami, 16 month grana padona, Braised veal ossobuco, whitepolenta, Kenya beans, porcini, red grape', '', 'Biscotti is a fun, contemporary Italian restaurant in Bangkok. With its open kitchen, Biscotti offers an intimate fine dining experience in Bangkok where guests can watch the chefs and enjoy the aroma of home-cooked food.', 'A minute’s walk from Ratchadamri Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2930, 'en_US', 'Thiptara - The Peninsula Hotel', 'Thiptara, the signature Thai restaurant of the Peninsula Hotel, Bangkok.', 'Three flavors snow fish, Pandan Chicken, Khan Thoke', '', 'Thiptara set on teak decking around a banyan tree, each holds just two tables, ensuring intimate dining by candlelight, or sit at open river bank tables for a sublime view. Forget you’re in the middle of Bangkok.', 'A 5-minutes by free ferry transfer from Saphan Taksin BTS Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2931, 'en_US', 'Mei Jiang - The Peninsula Hotel', 'An award-winning Cantonese restaurant with river views and private rooms.', 'Dim sum, Deep-fried crispy fillet of snow fish with home-made dried shrimps and chilli salt, Wok-fried diced beef tenderloin in black pepper paste', '', 'Executive Chinese Chef Jackie Ho heads the kitchen at Mei Jiang where his utmost respect for tradition is tastefully fused with creativity to produce a menu with dishes that range from classic dim sum fare to innovative dishes such as roasted pigeon marin.', 'A 5-minutes by free ferry transfer from Saphan Taksin BTS Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2932, 'en_US', 'River Cafe & Terrace - The Peninsula Hotel', 'Invite to experience the world on a plate with an impressive selection of dishes', 'Salmon, Wagyu Beef, Grilled Scallop', '', 'The River Cafe & Terrace\'s ever-popular buffets invites diners to experience the world on a plate with an impressive selection of dishes, specially prepared by a stellar team of multinational chefs.', 'A 5-minutes by free ferry transfer from Saphan Taksin BTS Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2933, 'en_US', 'The Lobby - The Peninsula Hotel', 'Afternoon Tea is served at The Lobby, \naccompanied by live music.', 'Traditional Afternoon Tea Set, Thai Afternoon Tea Set, Scone', '', 'In time honoured tradition,The Peninsula’s renowned Afternoon Tea is served at The Lobby, accompanied by live music. An all-day, a la carte menu is also ideal for breakfast, power lunches or a light, sophisticated dinner.', 'A 5-minutes by free ferry transfer from Saphan Taksin BTS Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2934, 'en_US', 'Sirocco  - The Lebua Hotel', 'Sirocco, the world\'s tallest open-air Mediterranean restaurant.', 'Perigord foie gras duo, 24-hour braised wagyu beef short rib, Maine lobster', '', 'Sirocco, the world\'s tallest open-air Mediterranean restaurant. More epicurean delights await at Distil lounge, our celebrated Asian restaurant Breeze, and Mezzaluna, the fine-dining mecca acclaimed for its innovative cuisine.', 'A free shuttle to Saphan Taksin BTS Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2935, 'en_US', 'Madison - Four Seasons Hotel', 'The American steakhouse in Bangkok.', 'Australian wagyu tomahawk, Dover sole with anchovy truffle butter sauce, Roasted foie gras with onion compote', '', 'Located at the Four Seasons hotel, this American steakhouse is cosy yet elegant. The steak here are selected from all over the world.  The lounge with a built-in fireplace is a great spot for before or after meal&drinks.', 'A minute’s walk from Ratchadamri Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2936, 'en_US', 'Shintaro - Four Seasons Hotel', 'Trendy Japanese Restaurant which serves a first Class Sushi.', 'Harajuku Sashimi Set, Foie Gras, Seafood Salad', '', 'The food is trendy-Japanese, with dishes like sushi-pizza and California rolls that you wouldn’t find in a more traditional restaurant. Attentive but unobtrusive service makes it an ideal place for media-types to sit around and gossip.', 'A minute’s walk from Ratchadamri Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2937, 'en_US', 'Spice Market  - Four Seasons Hotel', 'Bangkok\'s famous Spice Market Restaurant.', 'Thai Spicy dipping sauce with fried fish, Mas sa man, Crab curry', '', 'The menu is extensive and features dishes from the four regions - each with its own unique influences - but focusing on Central Thailand. Every taste is catered for, with a variety of fish, pork, beef, chicken and vegetarian dishes - as well as fresh fruits and a selection of delectable desserts.', 'A minute’s walk from Ratchadamri Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2938, 'en_US', 'Voila - Sofitel Bangkok Sukhumvit', 'The lunch&dinner buffets offer an array of French Inspired and Asian cuisines.', 'Pan-fried Foie gras, Alaska King Crab, Lobster, Dessert of the day', '', 'Voilà! is Sofitel Sukhumvit\'s signature all day dining venue. At the renowned Sukhumvit restaurant, you can savour gourmet cuisine with delectable dishes prepared by passionate chefs at live cooking stations.', 'A 10-minutes walk from Asoke and Nana BTS Skytrain stations, as well as Sukhumvit MRT Subway Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2939, 'en_US', 'Bai Yun - Banyan Tree Bangkok', 'Bangkok\'s oriental restaurant among the clouds.', 'Crispy Prawn Taro nest, Fresh milk stream bun', '', 'With deliciously modern twists on classic Cantonese recipes and a wonderful tea list complete with the every nourishing selection and the expertise of an in-house tea sommelier, prepare to delight your palate with a medley of gorgeously prepared Chinese fare.', 'A 10-minute walk from Lumphini MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2941, 'en_US', 'Romsai - Banyan Tree Bangkok', 'The very best of Asian and global cuisines.', 'Peking Duck, Grilled River Prawn', '', 'An all-day international restaurant offering a full à la carte menu and temptingly palatable buffet spreads that include enormous salad selection, cold and roasted meats,and superbly cooked fresh seafood.', 'A 10-minute walk from Lumphini MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2942, 'en_US', 'Vertigo  - Banyan Tree Bangkok', 'Enjoy an al fresco roof top dining experience high above the city.', 'Wagyu Beef Steak, Cannelloni mushroom & spinach, Andaman Prawn', '', 'Vertigo offers an al fresco dining experience set atop a roof terrace overlooking the glittering cityscape of Bangkok – a grill-and-bar experience that is Asia\'s first. Dine on fork-tender seafood and premium steaks while feasting your eyes on the city\'s vast skyline.', 'A 10-minute walk from Lumphini MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2943, 'en_US', 'Saffron - Banyan Tree Bangkok', 'Serving signature contemporary Thai cuisine.', 'Stream Snow fish with lime, Massaman Beef, Roasted duck curry', '', 'A contemporary décor to suit the contemporary palate, Saffron is located on the 52nd floor and boasts sublime views of Bangkok City. Come here to enjoy the best atmosphere and taste the best Thai food.', 'A 10-minute walk from Lumphini MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2944, 'en_US', 'Lin-Fa Chinese Restaurant - The Sukosol', 'The spectacular dim sum that you will never forget.', 'Dim sum, Peking duck, Dried fish maw in brown sauce', '', 'Chef Ruean of Lin-Fa Chinese Restaurant shows us the art of dim sum. It seems to be very simple, but you need a lot of practice, experience and heart. Chef cares about every little detail to serve you spectacular dim sum that you will never forget!', 'Located next to Phaya Thai BTS station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2945, 'en_US', 'Patummat International Restaurant - The Sukosol', 'The best of Asian and International cuisine in all-day restaurant.', 'Salmon sashimi, Salmon terrine', '', 'All-day dining restaurant serving breakfast, lunch/brunch and dinner buffets and à la carte meals. With Thai, Western and Asian cuisine changed daily to ensure variety, and an extensive selection of meat, seafood, cheese and desserts on offer.', 'Located next to Phaya Thai BTS station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2946, 'en_US', 'Yuan Chinese Restaurant - Millennium Hilton Bangkok', 'Contemporary Cantonese cuisine.', 'Stream Sea-bass with lime, Alabone soup, stewed pork rib with mushrooms', '', 'Oak furniture, velvet-cushioned chairs and silk tablecloths complete the theme. The air of sophistication is completed by the contemporary Cantonese cuisine at the Millennium Hilton Bangkok hotel.', 'Free shuttle boat service from its private pier to Saphan Taksin BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2947, 'en_US', 'Prime Restaurant  - Millennium Hilton Bangkok', 'The hotel\'s sophisticated steakhouse.', 'New York Strip Loin, Cream of wild mushroom and bergamot, Prime roasted beef', '', 'Soft tones create a relaxed ambience at the hotel\'s sophisticated steakhouse. Sip new and old world wines, savor the finest imported beef or choose fresh live lobster and oysters for dinner in this contemporary restaurant which looks out over the river.', 'Free shuttle boat service from its private pier to Saphan Taksin BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2949, 'en_US', 'Flow Restaurant - Millennium Hilton Bangkok', 'Contemporary restaurant for all-day dining from around the globe.', 'US Oyster, Hamaji, Grilled lamb', '', 'Join guests in this contemporary restaurant for all-day dining from around the globe. Enjoy stunning river views from the terrace and watch the chefs prepare sushi and sashimi specials in the open kitchen at this Bangkok restaurant.', 'Free shuttle boat service from its private pier to Saphan Taksin BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2951, 'en_US', 'Rang Mahal - The Rembrandt Hotel Bangkok', 'Delicious indian dishes with world\'s award.', 'Tandoori prawn/chicken, Raan-e-khyber, Jheenga kadhai, Dal maa Rang Mahal', '', 'Delicious, mouth-watering authentic Indian dishes created in a carousel of complementary flavors, tastes and colours served by welcoming staff against a spectacular skyline view of Bangkok.', 'A 10-minute walk from Asoke BTS Skytrain Station and Sukhumvit MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2952, 'en_US', 'Señor Pico - The Rembrandt Hotel Bangkok', 'Awarded Best Mexican Restaurant in Thailand status.', 'Quesadilla, Supreme fajitas, Espetada', '', 'A modern Mexican and Tequila Bar featuring authentic, tasty Mexican dishes and regional specialties and a selection of over 60 different tequila. Highlighted by spicy flavors, delightful textures, and garden-fresh local produce.', 'A 10-minute walk from Asoke BTS Skytrain Station and Sukhumvit MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2953, 'en_US', 'Flavours - The Rembrandt Hotel Bangkok', 'Flavours offers a wide range of cuisines from exotic Thai to Western classics', 'Smoked ham, Shrimp Cocktail, Oyster, Crab meat Lasagna', '', 'Flavours offers a wide range of cuisines ranging from exotic Thai dishes to Western classics.  A highlight is its extensive breakfast buffet featuring a panorama of genuine Asian and Western dishes complete with a live egg station, extensive Asian corner, live bakery and a walk-in deli.', 'A 10-minute walk from Asoke BTS Skytrain Station and Sukhumvit MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2955, 'en_US', 'La Scala - The Sukhothai Bangkok', 'Classical Italian cuisine in Thai atmosphere.', 'Saffron taglioni with crab, Scallops rossini, Stiacciatina', '', 'La Scala is a triumph of innovative interior design paired with classical Italian cuisine, perfectly concocted. Just as the design and decor unite the contemporary with a Thai cultural context, so the cuisine presents pure traditional recipes with unparalleled creative flair.', '10-minute walk from Lumphini MRT Subway Station, Close to Immagration Department', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2956, 'en_US', 'Celadon - The Sukhothai Bangkok', 'Serving Thai cuisine the way it was meant to be.', 'Pomelo Spicy Salad, Stream Snow fish with Stired fired Krachai', '', 'Named as the “Best Restaurant in Bangkok” by Travel and Leisure magazine, Celadon is a celebration of the senses - in true Thai style and service. Celadon serves authentic Thai cuisine in beautifully crafted air-conditioned salas.', '10-minute walk from Lumphini MRT Subway Station, Close to Immagration Department', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2957, 'en_US', 'Colonnade - The Sukhothai Bangkok', 'An epicurean discovery.', 'Lobster Bisque, Handmade coated chocolate, Spaghetti Pesto Sauce', '', 'Colonnade caters to all your whims with its dining menu that presents a staggering array of international cuisine. In an ambiance of casual elegance, epicures can enjoy live cooking, oyster shucking and sushi-making during the day.', '10-minute walk from Lumphini MRT Subway Station, Close to Immagration Department', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2958, 'en_US', 'Marriott Cafe - JW Marriott Hotel Bangkok', 'Simply incredible and masterfully presented', 'Lamb, Foie Gras, Oyster', '', 'Simply incredible and masterfully presented, this award-winning restaurant is sure to delight your taste buds. With its elaborate breakfast, lunch and dinner buffets and abundant à la carte menu, Marriott Café is the choice for fine casual dining.', 'A 5-minute walk from Ploenchit and Nana BTS Skytrain stations', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2959, 'en_US', 'Tsu Japanese Restaurant - JW Marriott Hotel Bangkok', 'Best Japanese restaurant in Bangkok.', 'Salmon Roll, Alaska King Crab, Engawa Sushi', '', 'Depart from the ordinary Japanese restaurant in Bangkok and step into exquisite dining at Tsu Japanese Restaurant. This dynamic dining experience serves only the finest, freshly prepared sushi within a contemporary atmosphere that is sure to delight.', 'A 5-minute walk from Ploenchit and Nana BTS Skytrain stations', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2960, 'en_US', 'Man Ho Chinese Restaurant - JW Marriott Hotel Bangkok', 'Authentic Chinese cuisine.', 'Peking Duck, Mango Pudding, Barbecued suckling pig', '', 'Authentic Chinese cuisine is one of the premier qualities of Man Ho Chinese Restaurant. The Cantonese, Szechuan and dim sum delights created by our master chef have made Man Ho an attraction to food enthusiasts everywhere.', 'A 5-minute walk from Ploenchit and Nana BTS Skytrain stations', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2961, 'en_US', 'Red Sky - Centara Grand & Bangkok Convention Centre', 'An enchanting experience for any diner longing.', 'Lobster Risotto, Crab Cake, Fillet of White Atlantic Halibut, Olive oil poach, flash grilled Iberico Prok Loin', '', 'A relaxed urban bistro on the rooftop, where creative cuisine and stunning vistas combine to offer a memorable dining experience. Whether dining in air-conditioned comfort indoors, or in the dramatic outdoor setting.', 'A 10-minute stroll from Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2962, 'en_US', 'Fifty Five - Centara Grand & Bangkok Convention Centre', 'An exquisite selection of dishes.', 'Charcoal grilled USDA prime tenderloin, Pan seared duck foie gras with saffron pear, Smoked Salmon, creamy chantarelles', '', 'Phenomenal 360-degree views of the city skyline present a dramatic backdrop for an exceptional rooftop dining experience.  Indulge in an exquisite selection of prime steak, fine seafood dishes and signature offerings.', 'A 10-minute stroll from Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2963, 'en_US', 'The World - Centara Grand & Bangkok Convention Centre', 'Dine around the world and take in the flavours of local specialities.', 'Thai Spicy Dipping, Foie Gras, Pomelo Spicy Salad', '', 'Dine around the world and take in the flavours of local specialities and French, Japanese, Indian and Chinese cuisines showcased through the extensive a la carte menu and buffet stations.', 'A 10-minute stroll from Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2964, 'en_US', 'Ginger - Centara Grand & Bangkok Convention Centre', 'Rediscover the flavours of classical Chinese and Japanese cuisines.', 'Fried Shrimp with chilli and salt, Red BBQ Pork, Roasted Duck', '', 'Presented as themed buffets or from an extensive a la carte menu, and featuring star ingredients ranging from Japanese Wagyu Beef and Hokkaido King Crab to Phuket Lobster.', 'A 10-minute stroll from Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2965, 'en_US', 'Feast - Royal Orchid Sheraton Hotel & Towers', 'Interactive cooking stations preparing made-to-order items.', 'Foie Gras Topped with Mango Sauce, Oyster, Lobster', '', 'The restaurant is offering buffet and a la carte menu for breakfast, lunch and dinner with a wide variety of food from around the world including Thai, Chinese, Japanese, Indian and Western.', 'Free shuttle boats bring guests to Saphan Taksin BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2966, 'en_US', 'New York Steakhouse - JW Marriott Hotel Bangkok', 'The most exquisite steakhouse in Bangkok.', 'Caesar salad, US prime surf and turf, Tomahawk wagyu roast beef for two', '', 'The best steaks in town are served at New York Steakhouse, the most exquisite steakhouse in Bangkok. We serve only the finest steaks, mouth-watering sides and an array of superb seafood, all perfectly matched with an extensive wine collection.', 'A 5-minute walk from Ploenchit and Nana BTS Skytrain stations', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2967, 'en_US', 'The Reflexions - Plaza Athénée Bangkok, A Royal Méridien Hotel', 'Discover your passion for the unexpected.', 'Maine lobster with lemon balm and beetroot, Wagyu beef duo, Chocolate and mandarin parfait', '', 'A modern French restaurant with a passionate and personalised service focused on the discovery of taste and the connection of food and art.', 'BTS Phleon Chit Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2968, 'en_US', 'Silk Road - Plaza Athénée Bangkok, A Royal Méridien Hotel', 'Enjoy authentic Cantonese and other regional Chinese cuisines.', 'Peking Duck, Silk Shrimp, Crab Leg', '', 'Only the most prime, fresh ingredients are used to create classic dishes and chef’s creations alike. Stylish Shanghai-evoking décor strikes a subtle balance between past and present.', 'BTS Phleon Chit Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2969, 'en_US', 'Smooth Curry - Plaza Athénée Bangkok, A Royal Méridien Hotel', 'Traditional Thai dishes from the country\'s four regions.', 'Beef cheek massaman, Roasted Duck curry, Mango Sticky Rice', '', 'The authentic taste of Thailand can be discovered at Smooth Curry. Chef Jasvir Sangkhera has developed the cooking and fruit carving skills with many royal chefs. We have created new dishes that draw on the culinary heritage of Royal Thai cuisine.', 'BTS Phleon Chit Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2970, 'en_US', 'Utage - Plaza Athénée Bangkok, A Royal Méridien Hotel', 'Discover the culinary landscape of Japan for a business lunch or dinner.', 'Land of the rising star', '', 'Each dish is beautifully executed, and expresses Chef Samart Suphan\'s artistic flair as well as over two decades of experience. Utage features two private dining rooms, each can accommodate eight guests.', 'BTS Phleon Chit Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2971, 'en_US', 'Heichinrou  - Amari Watergate Bangkok', 'Emporor style southern Chinese cuisine', 'Barbecued peking duck, Deep-fried bean curd, Prawn mayonnaise', '', 'Feast on the fabled specialities of southern Chinese cuisine, including a selection of tasty Dim sum delicacies, prepared by Cantonese Master Chef Yiu Chi Chow. For special occasions, choose to dine in one of our elegent private rooms.', 'Nearby Platinum Fashion Mall', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2972, 'en_US', 'Thai on 4 - Amari Watergate Bangkok', 'A culinary journey of royal Thai cuisine.', 'Beef Green curry with Roti, Pomeo Spicy salad with Tiger prawn', '', 'Discover the flavours of ancient Siam in a stylish, modern setting. Spicy salads, delectable curries and fragrant soups for your palate’s pleasure.', 'Nearby Platinum Fashion Mall', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2973, 'en_US', 'Promenade - Amari Watergate Bangkok', 'Delicious daytime dining.', 'Smoked Salmon, Pizza, Almond Chicken', '', 'Tantalise your taste buds with our extensive range of international favourites served buffet style. Enjoy Asian and western specialities and a range of tempting desserts.', 'Nearby Platinum Fashion Mall', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2974, 'en_US', 'Henry J. Bean’s Bar & Grill - Amari Watergate Bangkok', 'American-style barbecue from the sizzling grill.', 'Hamburger, Buffalo Wings, Beef tenderloin', '', 'Authentic all-American style Henry J. Bean’s Bar and Grill opens late and closes even later. Part of the noted worldwide chain, Henry J. Bean’s offers a fun and relaxed atmosphere.', 'Nearby Platinum Fashion Mall', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2975, 'en_US', 'Cascade - Amari Watergate Bangkok', 'Relax in the chilled out atmosphere hippest new dining venue.', 'Sesame chicken with Sweet pepper sauce, Garlic Herb Penne with Shrimp, Deep Fried Squid', '', 'Enjoy smooth tunes in a laid back street café atmosphere and watch the world go by with your favourite beverage in hand. Snack upon a variety of sumptuous offerings - including baked goods, deli items, and other delicious appetisers.', 'Nearby Platinum Fashion Mall', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2976, 'en_US', 'Yamazato - Okura Prestige Hotel', 'Experience unforgettable authentic flavours here.', 'Kaiseki Ryuki, 7 Sashimi, Shokado Bento Box', '', 'Inspired modern cuisine at the hotel’s three fine dining restaurants embracing Japanese haute cuisine at Yamazato, ‘modern logical cuisine’ at Elements and endless varieties of Asian and western dishes at our all day dining venue Up & Above.', 'Located next to BTS Ploenchit', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2977, 'en_US', 'The Kitchen Table - W Bangkok', 'East meets West and Raw plays with cooked.', 'Pan-fried fillet of salmon with eggplant puree and capers, Pappardelle with duck ragu and pecorino cheese, Pizza with wild mushroom, goat cheese, truffle oil and rocket', '', 'The Kitchen Table brings the essence of a Modern Bistro. The journey begins with a full breakfast buffet of Western and Asian dishes.At lunch the aim is to bring calmness within a venue or simply recover from the stress of the urban city life.In the evenings, we set The Kitchen Table reveals the more Gourmet side of a Bistro.', 'A 3-minute walk from Chong Nonsi BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2978, 'en_US', 'The Emporia Restaurant - Emporium Suites by Chatrium', 'The Emporia has all day international cuisine.', 'Chicken fried rice, Wonton soup', '', 'Dine above the city with beautiful views at the Emporia Restaurant. Indulge with all your favourites, from our freshly prepared breakfast buffet, to creative Cantonese delights, to delicate dim sum lunches. There’s also a delicious range of international cuisine and all-day dining available.', 'Directly connected to Phrom Phong BTS Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2979, 'en_US', 'River Barge  - Chatrium Residence Riverside Bangkok', 'The Nightly Wow Concept offers a special ingredient of the day.', 'Salmon Steak, Cocktail Shrimp, Cheese Cake', '', 'Dine beside the ebb and flow of the Chao Phraya River as you sip and taste your way through an à la carte menu of Thai and international favourites. Taste the best food and enjoy the best view.', 'A free shuttle boat services to the BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2980, 'en_US', 'Trader Vic’s - Anantara Bangkok Riverside', 'Enjoy exotic culinary journeys that are enhanced by fantastic daily live music.', 'Barbecued St Louis spare ribs, Wood-fired New York strip steak, Crispy half-duck served tableside', '', 'Trader Vic’s serves the finest Pacific Rim cuisine, including unique tastes cooked in Bangkok’s only Chinese wood fired oven. Enjoy riverside view while sipping cocktails here is also a good idea.', '- A scheduled private boat shuttle takes guests to Saphan Taksin Skytrain station.\n- A 5-minute drive from new Krung Thon Buri Skytrain station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2981, 'en_US', 'Brio - Anantara Bangkok Riverside', 'Fresh handmade pasta, pizzas from the wood-fired oven.', 'Lobster Ravioli, Roasted Rack of Lamb', '', 'Fresh handmade pasta, pizzas from the wood-fired oven, savoury Italian appetisers, all served in an inviting Tuscan villa setting. Designed to emulate the Italian countryside, Brio’s terracotta and sandstone décor is accented with subtle splashes of colour.', '- A scheduled private boat shuttle takes guests to Saphan Taksin Skytrain station.\n- A 5-minute drive from new Krung Thon Buri Skytrain station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2982, 'en_US', 'Benihana - Anantara Bangkok Riverside', 'Enjoying the performance of the Teppanyaki cooking style.', 'Chirashi, Dragon Roll, Tai Ceviche', '', 'The renowned Japanese Teppanyaki steakhouse, Benihana lives up to all the entertainment and culinary excellence of its reputation. Marvel as personal chefs prepare seafood, meats and vegetables, grilling them to perfection right at your table.', '- A scheduled private boat shuttle takes guests to Saphan Taksin Skytrain station.\n- A 5-minute drive from new Krung Thon Buri Skytrain station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2983, 'en_US', 'Tapas Y Vino - Grand Millennium Sukhumvit Bangkok', 'The most popular Spanish restaurant in Bangkok.', 'Yellow fish curry, Ostrich sausages, Steamed sea bass', '', 'If you are a lover of wine, then you will immediately adore Tapas Y Vino with its exquisite selection of tasty tapas, great Spanish food and fine wines, not just from Spain but all over the world.', 'A 10-minute walk from Asoke BTS Skytrain Station and Sukhumvit MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2984, 'en_US', 'Atelier - Grand Millennium Sukhumvit Bangkok', 'Atelier Bangkok is an International Kitchen Theatre.', 'Grill Station, Cold Seafood', '', 'Atelier is French for \"workshop\". Hence this restaurant rattles and hums with the sights and sounds of dedicated specialist chefs, including masters of Cantonese and Indian cuisines, creating one original Thai, Indian, Chinese or Western delicacy after another.', 'A 10-minute walk from Asoke BTS Skytrain Station and Sukhumvit MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2985, 'en_US', 'Summer Palace - Intercontinental Bangkok', 'The finest Cantonese cuisine.', 'Deep-fried wasabi prawns, Coconut consomme with pork and abalone, Wok-fried garoupa with ginger and black bean', '', 'Summer Palace delivers the highest standards in Dim Sum, à la carte dining, Chinese Banquets and special occasions.', 'Adjacent to Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2986, 'en_US', 'Charm Thai - Intercontinental Bangkok', 'Authentic Thai cuisine.', 'Crispy Duck Curry, Stired fried soft-shell crab with kraprao, Massaman', '', 'Discover the authentic taste of Thailand at Charm Thai. Regarded as one of Bangkok’s best kept secrets by lovers of genuine Thai cuisine, Charm Thai invites you to a relaxed dinner in casual surroundings.', 'Adjacent to Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2987, 'en_US', 'Grossi Trattoria and Wine Bar - Intercontinental Bangkok', 'Italian charm with Australian spirit.', 'Spagetti Soft shell crab, Pappadelle  rague, Seafood Risotto', '', 'Guy’s partnership with InterContinental Bangkok brings his own unique style of Italian charm with Australian spirit to the heart of Bangkok.', 'Adjacent to Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2988, 'en_US', 'Fireplace Grill - Intercontinental Bangkok', 'Diners will enjoy relaxed, yet impeccable service at Fireplace Grill.', 'Carpaccio of tuna, Duet of wagyu, Grilled loin of lamb', '', 'Start the dinner with one of our signature cocktail, then select one of the many prime steak cuts and French classics paired perfectly with an outstanding and well balanced wine list.', 'Adjacent to Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2989, 'en_US', 'Espresso - Intercontinental Bangkok', 'Each serving prepared to order by our talented chefs.', 'Alaska King Crab, Wagyu Beef, Foie Gras', '', 'Our well renowned all day dining venue ensures an innovative take on buffet dining with a host of live cooking stations, each serving delicious à la minute cuisine prepared to order by our talented chefs.', 'Adjacent to Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2990, 'en_US', 'Rib Room and Bar - The Landmark Bangkok', 'Bangkok\'s award winning steak house.', 'Tournedos rossini, Australian grain-fed beef, Pan-fried foie gras', '', 'Award-winning rooftop restaurant specializes in steakhouse favorites and a long list of gourmet French cuisine prepared by the hotel’s Executive Chef in cutting-edge kitchens.', 'Nana BTS Skytrain Station at its doorstep', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2991, 'en_US', 'Park Society - Sofitel So Bangkok', 'Fine gastronomy meets spectacular views.', 'Foie gras 3 ways, Lamb 3 ways, Mizayaki wagyu steak, Chocolate lava cake', '', 'Fine gastronomy meets spectacular views. Captivate your senses as an array of surrounding city lights of Bangkok playfully converge into this chic rooftop restaurant and bar.', 'A 3-minute walk from Lumpini MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2992, 'en_US', 'Red Oven - Sofitel So Bangkok', 'A feast of international cuisine and free flowing wine.', 'Peking Duck, Streamed Snow fish with sauce', '', 'Reminiscent of traditional market-style food fare with a contemporary twist. Featuring an iconic Red Oven as a center piece and 3 distinguished zones of design, with live cooking stations and a wide selection of food, drinks and desserts.', 'A 3-minute walk from Lumpini MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2993, 'en_US', 'Le Normandie - Mandarin Oriental Bangkok', 'Imaginative French cuisine and opulent surroundings.', 'Poached foie gras, Carved challans duck, Blue lobster with mango and papaya', '', 'One of the best-loved French restaurants in Asia, Le Normandie offers a delicious fine dining menu and an exceptional wine cellar.', 'Mandarin Oriental Bangkok provides a free shuttle boat to Taksin BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2994, 'en_US', 'Lok Wah Hin - Novotel Bangkok Platinum', 'Traditional places in town to remember how delightful dim sum really can be.', 'Dim sum, Peking duck, Steamed grouper in brown sauce', '', 'The Best Chinese Restaurant in Bangkok, offers extensive array of creative discerning diners a vast array of over 400 delicacies from around China. Famous world-wide for its Peking Duck and Dim Sums, in a classical Chinese village style atmosphere.', 'A 12-minute walk to Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2995, 'en_US', 'Eve - Hansar Hotel', 'Menus serving seasonal and exquisite French Mediterranean cuisine.', 'Snow crab with cucumber jelly, Sea scallops three ways, Chilean sea bass with basil crust', '', 'Menus are created around the four seasons with a new weekly inspiration menu highlighting the most fresh and rare ingredients sourced from around the world.', 'A 3-minute walk from Rajdamri BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2996, 'en_US', 'Don Giovanni Italian Restaurant - Centara Grand at Central Plaza Ladprao', 'Authentic Italian cuisine.', 'Pan-roasted Australian beef tenderloin and grilled tiger prawn, Pan-fried snow fish with grilled vegetables, Grilled peppered Australian lamb rack', '', 'The warm, cosy setting of this trattoria-inspired restaurant perfectly complement the flavours of Italian cuisine. One of the jewels in Don Giovanni Italian Restaurant is our Italian Chef Stefano, who has taken it upon himself to please and impress with authentic dishes inspired by regional Italian home-style recipes.', 'A 10-minute walk from Phahonyothin MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2997, 'en_US', 'Dynasty Chinese Restaurant - Centara Grand at Central Plaza Ladprao', 'Authentic Chinese cuisine.', 'Peking Duck, Streamed Snow fish with sauce, Shark\'s fin', '', 'Dynasty brings a new dimension to authentic Chinese cuisine in northern Bangkok. Dynasty serves the wonderful flavours of home-style Cantonese cuisine and the delicacies of Imperial Chinese Era prepared by Hong Kong chefs.', 'A 10-minute walk from Phahonyothin MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2998, 'en_US', 'Blue Sky Rooftop Restaurant - Centara Grand at Central Plaza Ladprao', 'The most exciting lounging and dining destinations in this part of the city.', 'Tom Yam Lobster, Spaghetti fried with baby calm and crayfish, Foie Gras Salad with Truffle sauce', '', 'Blue Sky is set on the hotel’s rooftop, commanding an unobstructed perspective of the city skyline. Sit back and relax at dusk, indulge in light bites, wines of the world and signature drinks such as our Blue Angel Cocktail.', 'A 10-minute walk from Phahonyothin MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2999, 'en_US', 'Chatuchak Cafe - Centara Grand at Central Plaza Ladprao', 'Chatuchak Café is where Asian taste meets Western flavours.', 'Salmon Steak, Snipper, BQ Ribs', '', 'Highlights of your dining experience include a fabulous selection for breakfast, a choice of fresh seafood and grilled fish and meat. Take in the flavours of local specialities and French, Japanese, Indian and Chinese cuisines at the daily changing lunch and dinner buffets.', 'A 10-minute walk from Phahonyothin MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3000, 'en_US', 'Hagi Japanese Restaurant - Centara Grand at Central Plaza Ladprao', 'Modern and classcial Japanese cuisine', 'Sushi and Sashimi, Tepanyaki, Salt grilled Snow fish', '', 'Hagi’s menu presents carefully crafted Japanese specialities featuring seasonal ingredients. Dining at Hagi is a culinary delight, with signature offerings including a wide selection of sushi and sashimi.', 'A 10-minute walk from Phahonyothin MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3001, 'en_US', 'Le Danang Vietnamese Restaurant - Centara Grand at Central Plaza Ladprao', 'Authentic Vietnamese cuisine.', 'Asparagus and crab soup, Duck cheek with tammarind sauce, Avocado and crab salad', '', 'One of Bangkok’s most celebrated destinations for Vietnamese cuisine, Le Danang serves exquisite Vietnamese cuisine and specialities from the Da Nang region with an emphasis on seasonal offerings.', 'A 10-minute walk from Phahonyothin MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3002, 'en_US', 'Suan Bua Thai Restaurant - Centara Grand at Central Plaza Ladprao', 'Home-style Thai cuisine and Royal Thai specialities.', 'Fried soft shell crab with garlic and pepper, Grilled pork spare ribs marinated with honey, Sauteed mixed seafood with red curry paste served on a sizzling platter', '', 'Suan Bua’s menu of authentic Thai culinary delights includes century-old recipes and the flavours of Royal Thai cuisine, traditional som tum papaya salad, tangy Isan specialities, smooth curries, and a wide choice of locally sourced seafood prepared Thai-style with an array of spicy and flavourful dips.', 'A 10-minute walk from Phahonyothin MRT Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3004, 'en_US', 'Chon Thai - The Siam Hotel', 'Home-cooked Thai cuisine that you can\'t miss.', 'Gaeng chaplu poo, Pork Ribs, Somtum with Grilled Chicken', '', 'Chon is the Thai word for spoon: our very own symbol of service, dining and sharing. At The Siam’s signature Thai restaurant and cooking school, you will be served a truly, local meal while enjoying some fascinating history.', 'Free shuttle boat from Saphan Taksin BTS Station: The Siam boat docks at the \"Sheraton\" Pier. When facing the water under the bridge It\'s the third pier to the left.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3005, 'en_US', 'Deco Bar & Bistro - The Siam Hotel', 'Perfect place for casual chic dining the lively atmosphere of a bygone era.', 'Linguini Marinara, Chicken Schnitzels, Ocean Trout fillet', '', 'The snappy black & white interiors of Deco Bar & Bistro bring to life Thailand’s Art Deco period, with international comfort cuisine inspired by the jazzy ambiance.', 'Free shuttle boat from Saphan Taksin BTS Station: The Siam boat docks at the \"Sheraton\" Pier. When facing the water under the bridge It\'s the third pier to the left.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3006, 'en_US', 'The District Grill Room and Bar - Bangkok Marriott Hotel Sukhumvit', 'A modern fish and beef grill style restaurant.', 'Hot/iced district heights, Caesar salad, Tenderloin', '', 'A modern fish and beef grill style restaurant that celebrates culinary legacies with a showcase of classic dishes cooked the way they were meant to be served.', 'BTS Skytrain Thong Lo Station 0.1 miles', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3007, 'en_US', '57th Street - Bangkok Marriott Hotel Sukhumvit', 'The modern all-day dining restaurant.', 'River prawn topped with tammarind sauce, Tom Yam River Prawn', '', 'Bright, bold and upbeat, this modern all-day dining restaurant embodies the soul of home style cooking', 'BTS Skytrain Thong Lo Station 0.1 miles', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3008, 'en_US', 'L’Appart - Sofitel Bangkok Sukhumvit', 'Classic French cooking techniques for a truly memorable dining experience.', 'French onion soup, comte cheese, crunchy walnut bread, Steamed snow fish, king crab, black ink risotto', '', 'You can experience a contemporary approach to cuisine that skillfully marries local flavors with classic French cooking techniques for a truly memorable dining experience in Bangkok.', 'Located 500 metres from Asoke and Nana BTS Skytrain stations, as well as Sukhumvit MRT Subway Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3009, 'en_US', 'Angelini - Shangri-La Hotel', 'You will have a lasting impressions of Italy after dining here.', 'Filetto di manzo with grilled portobello mushroom, Rack of lamb with white polenta, Tortellini with parmesan', '', 'Discover why the restaurant has been voted the best Italian restaurant in Bangkok by readers of Bangkok Dining & Entertainment magazine for 12 years in a row.', 'Adjacent to Saphan Taksin BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3010, 'en_US', 'Salathip - Shangri-La Hotel', 'Enchanting feasts by the River of Kings.', 'NEUA KA TA ROAN, SOM TUM KHOR MOO YANG, TOM YAM KEIW GOONG', '', 'A quintessential Thai dining experience by the River of Kings. Savour authentic cuisine in Thai-style teak pavilions while enjoying classical Thai dance performances.', 'Adjacent to Saphan Taksin BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3011, 'en_US', 'NEXT 2 - Shangri-La Hotel', 'A plethora of exciting dishes.', 'Satay, NEXT2 club, Barbequed baby back pork ribs', '', 'Serving Bangkok’s famous buffets in a prime riverside setting, expect a market-style spread of various regional, along with Continental and Asian à la carte menus.', 'Adjacent to Saphan Taksin BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3012, 'en_US', 'Shang Palace - Shangri-La Hotel', 'The elegance of Cantonese cuisine.', 'STICKY RICE WITH CRAB MEAT, BUDDHA JUMPS OVER THE WALL', '', 'Shang Palace Restaurant focuses first and foremost on the authenticity of its Cantonese and regional dishes. Stylish décor and distinguished private rooms of ample space make Shang Palace an ideal venue for business or social gatherings.', 'Adjacent to Saphan Taksin BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3013, 'en_US', 'Medici - Hotel Muse Bangkok', 'A Multiple Award Winning Italian Restaurant in Bangkok.', 'L’antipasto di mare, Spaghetti biroldo, Panna cotta with passion fruit', '', 'Known to locals who enjoy Southern Italian home-cooking cuisine has made this Italian Restaurant in Bangkok a two year consecutive winner The Best Italian Restaurant in Bangkok by Thailand Tatler Magazine.', 'A few minutes’ walk from Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3014, 'en_US', 'Liu - Conrad Bangkok Hotel', 'Combines the traditions and cultures of China.', 'Stewed pork belly with black soy sauce with manto, Wok-fried diced abalone in oyster sauce, Sauteed grouper fillet with xo sauce', '', 'A neo-classic Chinese restaurant that blends the culture, traditions and cuisines of old China, including Cantonese, Shanghainese and Sichuan dishes, with new and contemporary interpretations', 'A 6-minute walk from Ploenchit BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3015, 'en_US', 'KiSara - Conrad Bangkok Hotel', 'Authentic Japanese tradition, culture and cuisine.', 'Scallop Tempura, Aburi Salmon Roll, Unagi Powerful Roll', '', 'KiSara resonates with authentic Japanese tradition, culture and cuisine. Dine on the freshest sushi and sashimi and enjoy a range of specialties cooked on a Teppanyaki table.', 'A 6-minute walk from Ploenchit BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3016, 'en_US', 'CAFÉ@2 - Conrad Bangkok Hotel', 'Enjoy a wide selection of international cuisine at Café@2.', 'Thenus, Smoked Salmon, Unagi Sushi', '', 'This vibrant restaurant serves the finest local and imported ingredients to create a range of dishes which are sure to delight. Enjoy the modern yet classic décor and watch the chefs at their live cooking stations as they prepare the delicious cuisine.', 'A 6-minute walk from Ploenchit BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3017, 'en_US', 'Jojo - St. Regis Bangkok', 'A distinctly modern restaurant.', 'Mediterranean octopus, eggplant cream, crispy panelle, Homemade ravioli, lamb confit, pecorino cheese and potato foam, Seared scallops and red mullet, braised fennel', '', 'The chic dining venue features a distinctly modern restaurant, high tables, and an intimate bar. Through the artistic use of sliding panels and ambient lighting, the visually compelling venue creates a changing character and atmosphere in which to enjoy inviting lunch and dinner menus.', 'Take a few mins walk from BTS Rajdamri station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3018, 'en_US', 'Viu - St. Regis Bangkok', 'Sunny environment that recalls the grace and character of a stately home.', 'Pumpkin & Beet root Salad, Lamb Green Curry with Rice, Local Seabass Fricaese', '', 'If you are in the mood for a deliciously indulgent morning meal, enjoy our special Astor Champagne breakfast . Or, you may wish to order from the St. Regis breakfast menu, with selections from eggs cooked to order and housemade breads and jams to Asian-style offerings. Including other dishes all day.', 'Take a few mins walk from BTS Rajdamri station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3019, 'en_US', 'Giorgio’s - Royal Orchid Sheraton Hotel & Towers', 'A delicious Italian cousine.', 'Burrata risotto, Seafood and rock lobster soup, Baked sea bream', '', 'This modern and charming Italian eatery sets the scene for a delicious experience savoring varied authentic cuisine and fine wines from our impressive list. An uncovered terrace overlooks the Chao Phraya River for a stimulating al fresco experience.', 'Get off at BTS Saphan Taksin Station. Once at Saphan Taksin, please take the exit 1 or 2 leading to the pier where the hotel complimentary shuttle boat will be leaving every 30 minutes from 10 am. to 10 pm.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3020, 'en_US', 'Thara Thong - Royal Orchid Sheraton Hotel & Towers', 'Royal Thai cuisine served with the hospitality&graceful customs of Thailand.', 'Lemongrass Salmon, Three tastes Shrimp, Pomelo spicy salad', '', 'In an exquisitely authentic setting featuring a hand-carved teakwood pavilion, live classical music, and floor seating, dinners comprise expertly prepared royal Thai cuisine served with the kind hospitality and graceful customs of Thailand.', 'Get off at BTS Saphan Taksin Station. Once at Saphan Taksin, please take the exit 1 or 2 leading to the pier where the hotel complimentary shuttle boat will be leaving every 30 minutes from 10 am. to 10 pm.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3021, 'en_US', 'Sambal Bar & Grill - Royal Orchid Sheraton Hotel & Towers', 'Chic and comfortable with al fresco riverside dining and bar.', 'Raw Tuna, Wrapped vegetable salad, Deep fried soft-shell crab', '', 'At Sambal Bar & Grill, understated worldliness gets a sensuous and friendly Southeast Asian welcome in a hip urban oasis with show kitchen and spacious terrace, for dining on freshly grilled meats and unsurpassed sweet and savory sauces along the Chao Phraya River.', 'Get off at BTS Saphan Taksin Station. Once at Saphan Taksin, please take the exit 1 or 2 leading to the pier where the hotel complimentary shuttle boat will be leaving every 30 minutes from 10 am. to 10 pm.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3022, 'en_US', 'Fei Ya - Renaissance Bangkok Ratchaprasong Hotel', 'Serving surprising Chinese cuisine.', 'Lychee-wood roasted peking duck, Deep-fried shiitake mushrooms, Lobster broth', '', 'You will find out why when you visit Fei Ya,winner of Thailands Best Restaurant Award. Serving modern and traditional Chinese cuisine with Northern specialties, Their signature is lychee wood roasted Peking duck.', 'Take a few mins walk from BTS Chit Lom station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3023, 'en_US', 'Flavors - Renaissance Bangkok Ratchaprasong Hotel', 'Serving the best International cuisine in Bangkok.', 'International crab hot, Goose dreep fry with Balsamic sauce', '', 'Flavors features an interactive, theatre-style kitchen serving internationally; Thai, Italian, Japanese, Indian, etc -influenced cuisine for breakfast, lunch, and dinner where you can taste different flavors all day.', 'Take a few mins walk from BTS Chit Lom station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3024, 'en_US', 'La Tavola & Wine Bar - Renaissance Bangkok Ratchaprasong Hotel', 'A signature Italian Restaurant.', 'Tuna Tatar, Sashimi tiger prawn, Grilled scallop with truffle sauce', '', 'Discover unexpected dining in Bangkok at La Tavola & Wine Bar, our signature Italian restaurant, offering fresh, inspired fare with fine wines to match. Also enjoy the Italian relaxing atmosphere.', 'Take a few mins walk from BTS Chit Lom station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3025, 'en_US', 'Crave - Aloft Bangkok Sukhumvit 11', 'Satisfies your appetite and delights your senses.', 'Fun-guy flatbread, Twice baked potato, Slow-braised Australian beef ribs with ginger, young tamarind leaves and mushroom soy', '', 'Bangkok has gone wild over Crave Wine Bar & Restaurant - the funky restaurant with a bold, new concept that blends style and technology with culinary creativity.', 'Free Tuk Tuk shuttles will zip you to and from the Nana BTS Skytrain or Sukhumvit MRT Stations', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3026, 'en_US', 'Thai Lao Yeh - CABOCHON Hotel', 'Featuring ever-popular Thai cuisine and introducing the Laotian fares.', 'Duck larb, Nahm prik ong, Aji fish dry curry', '', 'Original recipes combining the best of local cuisines will be presented to tease the taste buds gourmets while attempting to satiate the appetites of gourmands.', 'Take ten mins walk or Taxi from BTS Phrom Phong station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3027, 'en_US', 'La Vue - Siam@Siam Hotel', 'A French gastronomy restaurant.', 'Roasted turbot with sea asparagus, Duck confit with mushrooms, Challand duck breast with armagnac gravy', '', 'The law of gastronomy involving discovery, tasting, experiencing, researching, understanding and delivering sensory quality food for nutrition and enjoyment for every bite tasted in a dining experience.', 'Take five mins walk or Taxi from BTS National Stadium station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3028, 'en_US', 'Party House One - Siam@Siam Hotel', 'Party house  on projecting art and different style of music .', 'Seafood, Shrimp spicy sauce with vegetable, Grilled beef salad with jim jaw sauce', '', 'Party house one has an emphasism on projecting art and different style of music throughout the week, whether it be Swing Music, Blues, Electro Jazz or lounge in a chic artistic setting.', 'Take five mins walk or Taxi from BTS National Stadium station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3029, 'en_US', 'The Roof Restaurant - Siam@Siam Hotel', 'Thailand’s first stone grill alfresco restaurant.', 'Black Australian Angus Rib Eye of Beef, Atlantic Scallops, Live Maine Lobster', '', 'The Roof offers a variety of international dishes made from the world’s finest ingredients. Food is freshly cooked on volcanic stones which can retain the heat for a period of 20-minute cooking.', 'Take five mins walk or Taxi from BTS National Stadium station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3030, 'en_US', 'Breeze - The Lebua Hotel', 'Breeze is a testament to the rising stature of Asian cuisine among connoisseurs.', 'Chilean sea bass with chinese chives, Jasmine tea-smoked wagyu ribs, Steamed dim sum basket', '', 'Offering authentic yet impeccably innovative dishes from our award-winning chef in a stunning venue where design, cuisine and service come together for an evening unlike any other.', 'Take seven mins walk or Taxi from BTS Taksin Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3031, 'en_US', 'Café Mozu - The Lebua Hotel', 'Serving authentic Lebanese, Indian, Thai and Western dishes.', 'Japanese salad, Sushi buffet', '', 'Café Mozu serves authentic Lebanese, Indian, Thai and Western dishes with a contemporary presentation, prepared by chefs from each region in a theatrical expanse of crystal and crimson that is as dramatic as the cuisine.', 'Take seven mins walk or Taxi from BTS Taksin Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3032, 'en_US', 'Mezzaluna - The Lebua Hotel', 'The seasonally inspired tasting menus are reinvented each day.', 'Lobster & Scallop, Atlantic Turbot', '', 'Bangkok’s finest and highest restaurant on the 65th floor at Tower Club at lebua, where the breathtaking 180-degree city and river view are combining with the masterful culinary innovatively presented.', 'Take seven mins walk or Taxi from BTS Taksin Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3033, 'en_US', 'Coco\'s Cafe Restaurant - Bangkok Hotel Lotus Sukhumvit', 'One of Sukhumvit’s most iconic restaurants for over 20 years.', 'The dosa, Tom Kha Kai, Pla Sam Rod', '', 'The ambience is so fluid that Coco’s transforms from an all-day Asian dining concept during the day to an iconic international buffet in the evening and a modern poolside lounge for a weekend brunch.', 'Take ten mins walk or Taxi from BTS Phrom Phong station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3034, 'en_US', 'Scalini - Hilton Sukhumvit Hotel', 'Savor traditional Italian-American favorites and indulgent comfort foods.', 'lamb rack, beef carpaccio', '', 'Chic and relaxed, with a focus on fine foods and high-quality ingredients, this restaurant has a feature staircase, a vibrant open kitchen, tempting charcuterie and extensive food and wine displays.', 'Take exit 4 of Phrom Phong BTS station and only take 5 minutes walk', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3035, 'en_US', 'Mondo - Hilton Sukhumvit Hotel', 'Perfect place to meet with friends over a bottle of wine.', 'Crispy Yesterday Roast Polpette, Fried Whole Prawns in Tempura', '', 'The menu at this popular restaurant showcases tapas dishes with influences and flavors from all over the Mediterranean and Asia.  The restaurant also has a open kitchen which let you enjoy the taste and the atmosphere in the same time.', 'Take exit 4 of Phrom Phong BTS station and only take 5 minutes walk', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3036, 'en_US', 'Kisso - The Westin Grande Sukhumvit Bangkok', 'Serving seasonal variations in Japanese cuisine.', 'Snow fish with shoyu, Wagyu shabu shabu salad, Sashimi', '', 'At Kisso that same seasonal variation is reflected in ever-changing menu highlights based on the availability of ingredients imported fresh from Japan.', 'Take a few mins walk form BTS Asok station or MRT Sukhumwit station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3037, 'en_US', 'Seasonal Tastes - The Westin Grande Sukhumvit Bangkok', 'All day dining restaurant serving an range of gourmet international cuisine.', 'Smoked Salmon, Baked Chicken with Potato sauce', '', 'Seasonal Tastes emphasizes freshness and high quality ingredients for a modern health-conscious lifestyle. As much food as possible is cooked ‘a la minute\', and diners can expect authentic flavours and delicious dishes presented with flair and creativity.', 'Take a few mins walk form BTS Asok station or MRT Sukhumwit station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3038, 'en_US', 'Medici Kitchen & Bar - Hotel Muse Bangkok', 'A Multiple Award Winning Italian Restaurant in Bangkok.', 'Rock lobster pasta', '', 'A rustic industrial space, a novel setting for a Award Winning Italian Restaurant in Bangkok. Known to locals who enjoy Southern Italian home-cooking cuisine has made this Italian Restaurant in Bangkok a two year consecutive winner The Best Italian Restaurant in Bangkok by Thailand Tatler Magazine.', 'Take seven mins walk or Taxi from BTS Chit Lom Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3039, 'en_US', 'Le Salon - Hotel Muse Bangkok', 'Enjoy signature Hotel Muse cocktails.', 'Hotel Muse cocktails, Oysters with Prosecco', '', 'Along with gourmet breakfast and lunch dishes, traditional afternoon tea awaits featuring sweet and savoury delights, while evenings mean a time to enjoy signature Hotel Muse cocktails, outstanding martinis, classic.', 'Take seven mins walk or Taxi from BTS Chit Lom Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
