(3041, 'en_US', 'Babette\'s The Steakhouse Bangkok - Hotel Muse Bangkok', 'Serving prime steak in the city against a glittering city backdrop.', 'French Scallop, Norway Salmon, Tiger prawn', '', 'Enter another era, with all its glitz and jazz – modern Art Deco interiors of a muted palette, comfy leather armchairs to sink into, clinking champagne flutes – a sultry ambience punctuated with the riff of live Blues.', 'Take seven mins walk or Taxi from BTS Chit Lom Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3042, 'en_US', 'DINE@7 - Majestic Grande Hotel', 'Sparklingly modern restaurant in Bangkok.', 'Tuna in Coconut milk, Chicken green curry, Honey grilled pork', '', 'Lavish buffets are presented for breakfast, lunch and dinner, with a wide selection of Thai, Asian and international dishes which you can enjoy with various type of food moreover you can expriece the international buffet style.', '- Take Taxi or 10 mins walk from BTS Nana or Phrom Phong Station\n- 300 metres from both Nana and Ploen Chit BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3043, 'en_US', 'Tables Grill  - Grand Hyatt Erawan Hotel', 'Designed by the world renowned designer.', 'Scallop, Grilled beef, Tom Yam seafood', '', 'The Sunday Brunch menu includes a spread of all-time favourites, including Boston Lobster and Oysters on Ice, Lobster Bisque, Champagne Risotto, Sunday Roast, Flamed Tiger Prawns and much more.', 'Take a few mins walk from BTS Chit Lom station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
