(3045, 'en_US', 'Spasso Restaurant and Bar - Grand Hyatt Erawan Hotel', 'A Bangkok restaurant for authentic Italian cuisine.', 'Rocket Salad, Pamaham pizza, Grilled duck legs', '', 'Italian Chef presents a wide selection of dishes from regional specialties, pasta, salads to pizzas baked in a wood-fired oven. Your day will be changed here.', 'Take a few mins walk from BTS Chit Lom station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3046, 'en_US', 'The Dining Room - Grand Hyatt Erawan Hotel', 'Perfect for a light meal as well as a relaxing dining experience.', 'Peking Duck, Fried shrimp with spicy sauce, Pamaham', '', 'Featuring International, Thai and Asian cuisines, fresh seafood, Japanese corner and a steam counter for Asian dumplings. This international buffet can make you reach the real buffet feeling which all foods were made by fresh ingredients and serves hot to you.', 'Take a few mins walk from BTS Chit Lom station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3047, 'en_US', 'Erawan Tea Room - Grand Hyatt Erawan Hotel', 'Serves traditional Thai cuisine complemented.', 'Crab meat omelet, Green Curry, Chicken Puff', '', 'Take-away packaged products and a wide selection of teas from India, China, Sri Lanka, and Thailand are available. This Bangkok hotel restaurant serves Morning Tea, Lunch, Afternoon Tea and Dinner.', 'Take a few mins walk from BTS Chit Lom station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3048, 'en_US', 'Attico - Radisson Blu Plaza Bangkok', 'Providing breathtaking views of the city skyline.', 'Parma Ham, Berrada Cheese, Wagyu beef', '', 'Inside the restaurant, diners discover rustic wood features that combine with modern elements to create a warm, inviting atmosphere.', 'Take ten mins walk or Taxi from BTS Asok station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3049, 'en_US', 'China Table - Radisson Blu Plaza Bangkok', 'Innovative versions of Cantonese favorites.', 'Dim sum from vegetable garden, Din sum from the ground, Dim sum from the sky', '', 'Guests rave over the handcrafted noodles, glazed roast, tea-smoked duck and specialty dim sum bars, which are coupled perfectly with herbal Chinese teas.', 'Take ten mins walk or Taxi from BTS Asok station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3050, 'en_US', 'Twenty-Seven Bites - Radisson Blu Plaza Bangkok', 'Twenty-Seven Bites offers a chic, brasserie atmosphere that highlights local and regional flavors.', 'Alaska king crab, Imported shell, Grilled pork', '', 'Open all-day, Twenty-Seven Bites offers a chic, brasserie atmosphere that highlights local and regional flavors via buffets and à la carte menus. Begin each day with our signature Super Breakfast buffet, featuring interactive cooking stations with Vietnamese, Thai, Japanese, Chinese and Western favorites.', 'Take ten mins walk or Taxi from BTS Asok station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3051, 'en_US', 'The Living Room - Sheraton Grande Sukhumvit', 'Cocktails, Light Meal & Live Jazz', 'Deep fried squid tempura, Cheese cake with Rassberry', '', 'Bangkok\'s premier jazz venue hits all the right notes; The Living Room\'s lounge bar plays host to the best international jazz musicians every night—accompanied by a wide variety of specialty cocktails and delectable light meals.', 'Take one min walk from BTS Asok station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3053, 'en_US', 'Jin Chieng Seng - Inn A Day', 'A very relaxed experience with well executed Thai dishes.', 'Pad Thai Goong, Som Tam, Tom Yam Goong', '', 'The food was an excellent Thai cuisine and well priced, particularly when considered against some of the neighboring establishments that charge significantly more for being on the river. You can enjoy the silent of the river here and let the time pass.', 'Take four mins walk from Tatain station (Chao Phraya Express Boat)', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3054, 'en_US', 'The Great Kabab Factory - Majestic Grande Hotel', 'The nestled in the heart of Bangkok.', 'Lamb meat with Indian herb, Grilled fish with Indian onion', '', 'The Great Kabab FactoryTM is an Indian specialty restaurant that brings delectable Kababs from all over the Indian subcontinent to one table. Our ingredents is import fresh directly from Indai which even you are in Thailand but you can get the real feeling like you dining in India.', '- Take Taxi or 10 mins walk from BTS Nana or Phrom Phong Station\n- 300 metres from both Nana and Ploen Chit BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3055, 'en_US', 'Momo Cafe - Courtyard by Marriott Bangkok', 'Great Value Restaurant Near Chit Lom And Siam.', 'Fresh and fruity prawn and avocado salad, Thai Salmon Salad', '', 'Occupying a massive space, this restaurant feels very much like a hotel establishment, with high ceilings and floor-to-ceiling windows throughout – but without the inflated prices usually associated with hotel restaurants.', 'Take ten mins walk from BTS Rajdamri station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3056, 'en_US', 'Indulge - Sukhumvit Suites Hotel', 'Serving up Classic Dishes with unexpected twists!', 'Tofu Larb, Pomelo salad with prawns, Chicken satay', '', 'Indulge Restaurant offers a full bar menu, with an extensive wine list & creative cocktails that feature house-infused spirits. Just sit down, sip our drink, talk to your friends, and enjoy the best atmosphere. What do you want more?', 'Between Sukhumvit 21-23', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3057, 'en_US', 'Cotton Bar and Restaurant - Shanghai Mansion Bangkok', 'The hippest and jazziest venue in Bangkok and Chinatown.', 'Deep fried shrimp with bread, Deep fried angel mushrooms, Thousand gold shrimp rolls', '', 'You can lose yourself in great music, freshly minted cocktails, fine wine and food. Step up to Cotton, conveniently located in the center of Bangkok in Chinatown.', 'MRT-Hua Lam Phong Station (Exit 1) & 2 stops to BTS SkyTrain', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3058, 'en_US', 'Citrine Bar and Restaurant -  St. James Hotel', 'A fine selection of delicious international cuisine.', 'Roasted duck, Green curry fried rice, Scallops', '', 'The restaurant is charmingly surrounded by a landscaped walled garden, looking out to the swimming pool.The breakfast buffet is served from 05:00 to 10:30 hrs. and the à la carte menu is available for lunch and dinner.', 'Take fifteen mins walk or Taxi from BTS Phrom Phong station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3553, 'en_US', 'Noble House - Swissotel Nai Lert Park', 'Cantonese cuisine a its finest on the ground floor of a hotel.', '- Black Australian Angus Rib Eye of Beef- Atlantic Scallops- Live Maine Lobster', '', 'The famed dim sum buffet attracts guest from all over the city. Its unique design and cosy atmosphere will make it one of your favourite venues for both lunch and dinner.', 'Take 15 mins walk or Taxi from BTS Ploen Chit station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
