(3555, 'en_US', 'Rice & Chilli - Mode Sathorn Hotel', 'Thai Contemporary food.', 'Spicy fried grouper with Graprao, Lamb Massaman', '', 'Enjoy authentic Thai food served in a gastronomic style which is never seen  before in Bangkok. Dine on delicious dishes while relaxing in a lounge atmosphere and sipping on your choices of wine, creative cocktails and the pick of all that’s best.', 'Take one min walk from BTS Surasak station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
