(3562, 'en_US', 'Mezza - Park Plaza Bangkok Soi 18', 'Mezza delivers much more than your typical hotel café food.', 'Smoked Salmon Salad, Lobster Bisque, Shrimp Tapas', '', 'Mezza Restaurant, located the Park Plaza in Sukhumvit, specialises in combining Thai, international and Mediterranean culinary traditions to create innovative dishes. The restaurant also have abontdant of drinks waiting for you to try.', 'A 5-minute walk from Sukhumvit MRT Station and Asok BTS Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3563, 'en_US', 'Dee Lite - DoubleTree by Hilton Hotel Sukhumvit Bangkok', 'All day dining restaurant.', 'Delight Club, Beef Burger, Strawberry Millefeuille', '', 'Decorated in light fresh colors,with a focus on fresh, local dishes and quick and simple service, Dee Lite offers both indoor and outdoor seating and features a long open kitchen counter and freestanding juice and barista bars.', 'A 1-minute walk from Phrom Phong BTS Skytain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3564, 'en_US', 'Silver Waves - Chatrium Hotel Riverside Bangkok', 'One of the classiest ways to spend midday in Bangkok.', 'Crispy Roated Duck, Double Steamed Bird\'s Nest with Crab Claw', '', 'Literally dine above the Chao Phraya River at the stunning Silver Waves - perched high-up on the 36th floor, the views are truly breathtaking. The river inspired décor and authentic live entertainment provides a truly immersive culinary experience for you to indulge in the flavours of our Chinese delights.', 'A free shuttle boat services to the BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3565, 'en_US', 'Pier 28 - Chatrium Hotel Riverside Bangkok', 'The perfect place to chill out with the best of friends and family.', 'Cocktail, Steak, Sushi', '', 'Pier 28 is the perfect restaurant in Bangkok that offers fine dining style buffets, à la carte dining & cocktail drinks right beside the Chao Phraya River. Here is the place that you can enjoy not only the delicious menu but also beautiful scenary.', 'A free shuttle boat services to the BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3566, 'en_US', 'Wine Pub - Pullman Bangkok King Power', 'One of the best wine bars In Bangkok.', 'Lobster bisque, Tapas, French Oysters', '', 'Wine Pub Bangkok at Pullman Bangkok King Power merges a warm, relaxing and private space with the cool of the deep house music in the background and offers its guests a true international selection of wines individually selected by our sommelier.', 'A 10 mins walk from Phayathai Airport Rail Link, it has a free tuk-tuk shuttle from Victory Monument BTS Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3568, 'en_US', 'Cuisine Unplugged - Pullman Bangkok King Power', 'An all-day dining concept featuring an open kitchen.', 'Fresh Seafood, Beef Bourguignon, Foie gras', '', 'An all-day dining concept featuring an open kitchen with pizza, pasta, soup and noodle, dim sum, sushi, salad as well as home-made fresh breads and croissants.', 'A 10 mins walk from Phayathai Airport Rail Link, it has a free tuk-tuk shuttle from Victory Monument BTS Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
