(3571, 'en_US', 'MANGO 99 - Arnoma Hotel Bangkok', 'All day dining restaurant with modern Thai and International menus.', 'seafood on ice, sweet and sour fish', '', 'Mango 99 offers an extensive Breakfast Buffet, a wide selection of Thai and International specialties for Lunch and traditional Thai favorites for dinner.  Also choose from Asian, Western and Thai specialities available from A la Carte menu.', 'A 5-minute walk from Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3572, 'en_US', 'The Good Earth Restaurant - Arnoma Hotel Bangkok', 'One of the popular dim-sum buffet in Bangkok for many years', 'Dimsum, Steamed sea bass', '', 'The Good Earth restaurant continuously delights guests with superb Cantonese Food and Chinese delicacies crafted by our kitchen team. Worthy of special mention is our Dim Sum, prepared fresh daily and served for both lunch and dinner.', 'A 5-minute walk from Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3573, 'en_US', 'Trattoria Felice Italian Restaurant - Arnoma Hotel Bangkok', 'Serving Italian and European flavoured dishes.', 'Penne al\'arrabiata, Bucconini Alla Lucania, Rivera Pizza', '', 'Experience the casual atmosphere of our restaurant, serving Italian and European flavoured dishes. Happy with every menu by the skillful chef togehter with relaxing atmosphere in the restaurant.', 'A 5-minute walk from Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3574, 'en_US', 'Cafe De Nimes - Grand Sukhumvit Hotel Bangkok', 'All Day Dining Bangkok Restaurant at Cafe de Nimes.', 'fresh Seafood, Foie gras, Lamb', '', 'All Day Dining Bangkok Restaurant at Cafe de Nimes open 7 days a week for Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner, offering an array of themed Bangkok Buffet Promotion and both a Asian and International A la Carte menu to choose from.', 'A 5-minute walk from Nana BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3575, 'en_US', 'BonBon Delicatessen - Grand Sukhumvit Hotel Bangkok', 'Enjoy fresh made sandwiches, salads, chocolates, gourmet ice cream.', 'Chocolate Lava, Chocolate cup cake with chocolate milk, Smoked Salmon Sandwich', '', 'Bonbon Delicatessen located in the hotel lobby of this Sukhumvit Hotel is a bakery with the finest breads, pastries and cakes that are freshly baked daily on the premises.', 'A 5-minute walk from Nana BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
