(3579, 'en_US', 'Albricias Restaurant - Chatrium Sathon', 'The flavours of the Mediterranean.', 'Sea bass with tomato stew and coriander, Crab cake, Herbed Beef Carpaccio', '', 'Inspired by the flavours of the Mediterranean, here you’ll find mouthwatering French, Spanish, Italian and Greek cuisine. The restaurant is decorated in modern and elegant style which make you feel comfortable to sit in.', 'A free scheduled shuttle goes to Chong Nonsi BTS Skytrain Station.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
