(3581, 'en_US', 'Ocean Gastro Tapas Bar - Ocean Urban Lounge and Boutique Resort', 'High-quality dishes in a more friendly and convivial environment.', 'Champignon mushroom with parmesan foam and parsley oil, Raspberry yoghurt sponge', '', 'Ocean Gastro-Tapas Bar offers modern Mediterranean–Asian fusion cuisine. The concept behind the bar is called “bistronomy”—a genuine and more affordable approach to modern cuisine', 'Near BTS Phrom Phong', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3583, 'en_US', 'Huntsman Pub - The Landmark Bangkok', 'A nice and traditional british restaurant and pub.', 'Steak & kidney pie, Hungarian beef goulash soup, Grilled Flank Steak', '', 'Capturing the authentic atmosphere of a traditional British pub, this popular venue is famous for its chilled draught beer, expertly mixed cocktails and glorious food. Top sporting events are screened live on big screen TVs. The house band is one of Bangkok’s best.', 'Near BTS Nana Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3584, 'en_US', 'Greenhouse Restaurant - The Landmark Bangkok', 'Full flavors with a full view whether your taste is continental or oriental.', 'Congee, egg noodles with roasted duck, prawn dumplings', '', 'Our enduringly popular coffee shop offers local, Hong Kong noodle and congee, selection of Dim Sum, Asian and international. Make your menu never bored and delicious to the max.', 'Near BTS Nana Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
