(3586, 'en_US', 'Garden Court Restaurant - The Landmark Bangkok', 'East meets west in a cool garden atmosphere.', 'Scotland crab soup, sea bass with chili, peking duck', '', 'Relax in tropical furniture in a cool garden setting with towering palm trees. Choose from a comprehensive menu of fresh salads, delicious soups, burgers, fish and chips, pizzas, Bangkok’s best sandwiches, French pastries, home-made ice cream.', 'Near BTS Nana Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
