(3601, 'en_US', 'Tubtim Siam Thai Restaurant - Golden Tulip Sovereign Hotel', 'A fantastic choice of traditional Thai cuisine.', 'Pad Prik Khing, Tom Klong Snow fish, Pad Cha snow fish', '', 'Located on the 24th Floor of the hotel our superb Thai restaurant serves a fantastic choice of traditional Thai cuisine while viewing a panoramic view of the city\'s sky line. Culinary delights await you in an elegant ambience while being entertained by Thai classical music and dance.', 'Asok and Nana BTS Skytrain Stations, plus Taxi (not walking distance)', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
