(3608, 'en_US', 'Deck by the River - Arun Residence', 'Delicious among the beautifule river view', 'Millefeuille with Strawberries and Cream Mousse, Duck breast Salad, Pomelo Salad', '', 'Situated on the Chao Phraya across from Wat Arun, the Deck offers vivid views of one of Bangkok’s most beautiful temples. The restaurant’s Thai and international cuisine has made it a popular spot for tourists exploring historic Rattanakosin Island.', 'Wongwian Yai BTS Station, plus taxi (not walking distance)', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3609, 'en_US', 'Scandinavian Restaurant - Stable Lodge Hotel', 'The best Scandinavian food in Thailand.', 'Marinated herrings, Swedish Biff a la Rydberg-Fiskboller med asparges og blomkal', '', 'From the hot and spicy thrills of traditional Northeastern Thai cuisine to the familiarity of International, Scandinavian and European dishes, the restaurant at Stable Lodge on Sukhumvit offers mouth-watering specialities for all tastes.', 'A 5-minute walk from Nana BTS Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3610, 'en_US', 'Poolside Garden Restaurant - Stable Lodge Hotel', 'International dishes served in the Calm Comfort.', 'BIFF A LA RYDBERG, PORK CHOP WITH RED CABBAGE AND BOILED POTATOES, Fiskboller med asparges og blomkal', '', 'Unique to the Stable Lodge in the city centre is our tropical garden and lovely swimming pool.  Relax amidst tropical plants and trees and savour the lovely scent of exotic flowers in the cool of the evening by the pool.  Your cocktail will taste so much more delicious!', 'A 5-minute walk from Nana BTS Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3611, 'en_US', 'No. 43 Italian Bistro - Cape House', 'The finest in Italian prepared by Italian chefs.', 'pizza black truffle parma ham and marsapone, river prawns soaked and BBQd garlic coating', '', 'This restaurant brings the finest in Italian and Thai cuisine prepared by Italian chefs. The authentic, delicious and not so pricey dishes have made No. 43 a popular restaurant for lunchtime and evening diners. Dishes include pizzas, pastas, other main courses, cakes and ice cream.', '5 minutes walk from Chit Lom BTS station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3612, 'en_US', '100°East - Anantara Bangkok Sathorn', 'Asian and Western cuisine in a refined international environment.', 'Phad Thai, Hyderabad Biryani Chicken for Two, Salmon Steak', '', '100°East restaurant serves up an array of expertly prepared Asian and Western cuisine in a refined international environment, characterized by hardwood furniture and sensuous textiles', 'A free shuttle bus service to Chong Nonsi Skytrain Station is offered.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3613, 'en_US', 'ZOOM Sky Bar & Restaurant - Anantara Bangkok Sathorn', 'Meet, sip, dine and set new trends for a great night out on top of the city.', 'Thai style tuna ceviche, Sea bass, Beef tenderloin', '', 'This chicly designed chill out venue presents innovative experiences with 360º cityscape views.  Unwind at sunset with inspiring beverage and an extensive variety beverages and bar snacks.', 'A free shuttle bus service to Chong Nonsi Skytrain Station is offered.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3614, 'en_US', 'Crust - Anantara Bangkok Sathorn', 'The best pizzas Bangkok has to offer every night of the week.', 'Prawn Presto Pizza, seafood pizza', '', 'With its wood-fire pizza oven, Crust serves some of the best pizzas Bangkok has to offer every night of the week. Choose from a range of favourites or create your own topping at the pizza bar. Dinners can be enjoyed either at the bar, in 100°East or out on the pool deck.', 'A free shuttle bus service to Chong Nonsi Skytrain Station is offered.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3616, 'en_US', 'Grottino Swiss Restaurant - Grottino Residence', 'The Swedish traditional style in Bangkok', 'Swiss cheese fondue, Beef fondue Bourguignonne or Chinoise', '', 'The restaurant offers up to 30 seats in an indoor, air-conditioned non-smoking room and 20 seats on a cooled, outdoor smoking terrace which you can enjoy the real swedish dish which not only delicious but you also can enjoy the swedish atmosphere while you enjoying the dish.', '5 minutes walk from Asok BTS station and MRT Sukhumvit', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3618, 'en_US', 'Baiyoke Floating Market - Baiyoke Sky Hotel', 'An amazing array of Thai food with a fun theme for you to enjoy.', 'Tom Yam Gung, Pad Thai', '', 'The Baiyoke Floating Market is actually a novel idea, combining the fun of browsing at a market with the enjoyment of a Thai food buffet. The themed buffet style feels fresh and original and the food is as good as any you will find along the many waterways of Thailand', 'BTS Ratchathewi, plus taxi (not walking distance)', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
