(3620, 'en_US', 'The Mayflower - Dusit Thani Bangkok', 'The perfect mixture of East and West.', 'Dim Sum, Prawns with spicy sauce, Steamed crab claw', '', 'With its menu of Cantonese delicacies, The Mayflower is one of Bangkok\'s finest Chinese restaurants. Its luxurious interior is a combination of European design and Chinese antiques', '5 minutes walk from BTS Sala daeng and MRT Silom', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3621, 'en_US', 'Hamilton\'s Steak House - Dusit Thani Bangkok', 'Feast on the finest imported beef in our steak house.', 'Crab cakes, Wagyu tenderloin, Grilled lobster', '', 'With a wood-panelled interior that brings to mind 1920s New York City and a menu of the finest cuts of imported beef, Hamilton’s offers a scrumptious and relaxing escape from the bustle of Bangkok\'s streets.', '5 minutes walk from BTS Sala daeng and MRT Silom', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
