(4087, 'en_US', 'Ploy Restaurant - Grand Diamond Suites Hotel', 'Internationa buffet with various taste.', 'Sashimi, Grilled Saba, Deep fried pork', '', 'The casual International Cuisine restaurant, including Thai, Western and Halal food overlooking the pool has picture. It is warmly welcomed as if arriving at a friend’s home where the foods and flavors of East and West are blended to offer both unique luncheon and dinning experience.', 'Air Port Link Ratprarop and take taxi', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4088, 'en_US', 'Tae Chew Restaurant - Grand Diamond Suites Hotel', 'Chinese Cuisine specialties prepared by our celebrity chef from Hong Kong.', 'Shark\'s fin soup, Pra kradod Gampaeng', '', 'Savour the delightful Chinese Cuisine specialties prepared by our celebrity chef from Hong Kong. With signature dishes ranging from traditional recipes of Braised Superior Shark’s Fins Soup, specialty “Monk Jump Over the Wall”, roasted peking duck, dim sum etc.', 'Air Port Link Ratprarop and take taxi', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4089, 'en_US', 'Tai Fah Cafe - Grand China Hotel Bangkok', 'Décor of China Town.', 'Spicy seafood salad, Krapao pork, Fried rice', '', 'Asian and Western dishes are available at the Tai Fah Cafe, located on the 10th floor of the hotel and featuring a bright and contemporary decor. A buffet is served at meal times and a la carte is available all day.', 'MRT Hualumpong and take taxi', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4090, 'en_US', 'Sky View 360° - Grand China Hotel Bangkok', '360 degree environmental at this resturant.', 'German pork, Spaghettti cabonara, Rice with Chicken on top', '', 'Located on the top of the hotel, the Sky View 360° Restaurant offers fascinating views of the city and the Chao Phraya River, and is a wonderful place for international style dining and enjoying cocktails and cool drinks.', 'MRT Hualumpong and take taxi', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4091, 'en_US', 'Siang Ping Loh - Grand China Hotel Bangkok', 'Delicious Cantonese and Szechuan cuisine.', 'Hongkong Roasted Duck, Soup Jub Huey, Dim Sum', '', 'Siang Ping Loh Chinese Restaurant Serving Cantonese and Szechuan cuisines and with choice dim sum for lunch, this is a traditional Chinese restaurant with a cosy decor.  Private karaoke rooms with professional sound systems are part of the private room feature', 'MRT Hualumpong and take taxi', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4092, 'en_US', 'Benjamas Restaurant - Royal Benja Hotel', 'Different menu in each day to delight you.', 'Pizza, Sesami, Papaya salad', '', 'At Benjamas Restaurant, a wide selection of international cuisine are cooked to your satisfaction by top quality chefs and served in a cozy and friendly atmosphere. Whether your favourite dishes are traditional Thai, Western, Chinese, or Japanese foods.', 'Near BTS Nana', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4093, 'en_US', 'HIP Restaurants - Hip Bangkok', 'American style buffet that gurantee quality and delicious', 'Salad, Porridge', '', 'Various type of American breakfast which we serve fresh to you and let you enjoy evey dish that you taste from our menu. We care since prepare the ingredients process which will make evey dish still fresh and unlimited delicious.', 'Near MRT Huay Kwang', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4094, 'en_US', 'Veeranda - Suvarnabhumi Suite Airport Hotel', 'The best buffet resturant in Lat Krabang.', 'Grilled pork, Green curry, Tom Yam Goong, Tung Thong', '', 'The international food from Japan, Thai, China and Western, which chef prepare with fresh ingredients so it make every dish very delicious, moreover our restarant is a modern style and our service is very friendly welcome.', 'Suvahnaphumi Airport and take taxi', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4095, 'en_US', 'The Great Wall - Asia Hotel Bangkok', 'The best Cantonese of Ratchatewi.', 'Fried Bun, Roasted Duck, Ha Gao', '', 'One of Bangkok\'s premier chinese restaurant with a menu of exciting Cantonese specialities expertly prepared according to original recipe. Dim-Sum available at lunch and dinner.', 'Near BTS Ratchathewi Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4096, 'en_US', 'Tivoli - Asia Hotel Bangkok', 'Meet Thai food and Elvis at here.', 'Pad Thai, Sandwich, Pork Chop', '', 'Informal dinings any time of the day from an extensive menu offering an exciting variety of Thai, Regional and Continental favorites. Every night listen to the live music from the Thai Elvis Presley, Jareuk Viriyakij', 'Near BTS Ratchathewi Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4097, 'en_US', 'Saigon - Asia Hotel Bangkok', 'Enjoy a wide spread of buffet with 19 items to choose from.', 'Fresh spring rolls with salmon and vegetables, Grilled river prawns with lemongrass served with vermicelli, Grilled minced beef or pork wrapped in wild betel leaves', '', 'You can also enjoy a wide spread of buffet with 19 items to choose from, just to mention a few – Fresh Spring Rolls “Haiphong”, Sautéed Pork with Tomato & Lime Sauce, Chicken Curry Southern, Chilled Tapioca with Cantaloupe and milk etc', 'Near BTS Ratchathewi Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4099, 'en_US', 'Botanica - Indra Regent Hotel', 'Great garden views featuring all-day à la carte menu.', 'Green Chicken Curry, Satay', '', 'Decorated with rustic sandstone walls, ceiling-high gilded banana trees and a lush floral mural, this refreshing venue with great garden views features all-day à la carte menu.', 'A 10-minute walk from Ratchaprarop Airport Rail Link', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4100, 'en_US', 'Ming Court - Indra Regent Hotel', 'Serves a wide variety of authentic Chinese dishes.', 'Peking Duck, Dimsum, Dumbling', '', 'Named after the royal kitchen of the Ming Dynasty, Ming Court offers authentic Cantonese cuisine, Beijing specialties, and popular fare from other regions of China. A wide variety of Dim Sum is served during lunch and our a la carte.', 'A 10-minute walk from Ratchaprarop Airport Rail Link', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4102, 'en_US', 'Coffee Shop - The Emerald Hotel', 'Special “Boiled Rice” also served until midnight.', 'Seafood, Ceasar salad-Smoked Salmon', '', 'The Emerald Coffee Shop waits to welcome all Buffet Choice Seekers. Open around the clock, from early breakfast to late \"Khao Tom\" ,offering International Cuisine, Chinese delicacies and Thai favourites. A la carte also available.', '2 minutes’ walk from the MRT Huaykwang station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4103, 'en_US', 'Yok Chinese restaurant - The Emerald Hotel', 'A wide range of a la carte to a selection of set menus, and home made Dim Sum.', 'Ha Gao, Fried Spring Roll, Stream Spring Roll', '', 'Experience truly exquisite Chinese \"Cantonese\" Cuisine in our popular Chinese restaurant, from a wide range of a la carte to a selection of set menus, and home made Dim Sum. Here we will bring you enjoy not only the delicios taste of food but also out genuine chinese atmosphere.', '2 minutes’ walk from the MRT Huaykwang station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4104, 'en_US', 'Daiichi Japanese Restaurant - The Emerald Hotel', 'Indulge yourself with a large selection of culinary treats.', 'Sashimi, Shrimp Tempura, Grilled River Prawn', '', 'In a rare display of Japanese culinary heritage our private teppanyaki counter and intimate tatami rooms offer a memorable experience. Indulge yourself with a large selection of culinary treats from our daily buffet. A la carte also available', '2 minutes’ walk from the MRT Huaykwang station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4105, 'en_US', 'China Palace - Prince Palace Hotel', 'The restaurant of choice for authentic Chinese food in Bangkok.', 'Peking Duck, Fried Shirmp Salad, Goose Leg in Pot', '', 'China Palace presents their cuisine with the original formula of Hongkong-Chinese food styles including the Dim Sum and other classic Chinese culinary wonders. Set in a casual atmosphere, the Chinese interior design is mixed with breathtaking views of Bangkok from the 32nd floor.', 'Ratchathewi or National stadium BTS Station, plus taxi (not walking distance)', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4106, 'en_US', 'Krua Mahanak & Karaoke - Prince Palace Hotel', 'Enjoy the fantastic traditional Thai cuisine.', 'Nam Nueang, Pineapple fired rice, Mixed seafood Tom Yam, Grill Pork Bai Cha plu', '', 'Krua Mahanak Thailand Dining Cuisine is located on the 31st floor of the Prince Palace Hotel Bangkok with a good variety of recommended dishes, e.g. crispy fried chicken with herbs, roasted duck spring rolls, as well as a superb selection of traditional Thai cuisines', 'Ratchathewi or National stadium BTS Station, plus taxi (not walking distance)', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4107, 'en_US', 'Prince Cafe - Prince Palace Hotel', 'International cuisine is served in either buffet style or A-La-Carte.', 'Seafood, Steak', '', 'The interior is designed in a very relaxed manner and the services offered is great. A variety of salads, pizzas, pasta, steaks awaits to meet your international/western cuisine expectations. The Prince Cafe is situated at the 12th floor of the Prince Palace Hotel Bangkok.', 'Ratchathewi or National stadium BTS Station, plus taxi (not walking distance)', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4108, 'en_US', 'Shinsen Sushi Bar - Prince Palace Hotel', 'Famous for tepanyaki style cooking.', 'Tempura Soba, Tempura Roll, Salmon And Salmon Roe Don, Avocado Salad', '', 'An exquisite dining experience awaits at the Shinsen Sushi Bar Japanese Restaurant, which is located on the 11th floor of the Prince Palace Hotel Bangkok. We are ready to serve you the fresh ingredients that our Japanese chef design every menu to you.', 'Ratchathewi or National stadium BTS Station, plus taxi (not walking distance)', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4109, 'en_US', 'The Galleria - Ramada D\'MA Bangkok', 'An International Buffet for guests staying on qualified rate plans.', 'Spaghetti with spicy', '', 'The Galleria Restaurants offer a wide selection of International Cuisine. An International Breakfast Buffet is available for guests staying on qualified rate plans. All customer can enjoy the maximum delicious menu and taste at here only.', 'Opposite of the Makkasan Railway Station from which you can connect to the BTS Skytrain and MRT Subway station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4110, 'en_US', 'Charm Thai - Holiday Inn Bangkok Silom', 'Charm Thai is serving amazingly tasty Thai dishes.', 'Roasted Duck curry, Tom Yam Goong', '', 'Charm Thai at the Holiday Inn Bangkok, Ratchaprasong offers traditional Thai cuisine in an open “Asian Kitchen” ambience, with fresh new-look authentic Thai food for you to experience.', 'A 5-minute walk from Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4111, 'en_US', 'Cafe G - Holiday Inn Bangkok Silom', 'Best buffet restarant in Thailand', 'Spaghetti cream sauce, Cho Muang', '', 'Thai food buffet that served in market-style in relaxed atmosphere, with unlimited Coffee, Tea and Soft drinks!! With Pasta Station, Cake Corner, Noodle Station, Fruits and Salad and Soft drinks.', 'A 5-minute walk from Chit Lom BTS Skytrain Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4112, 'en_US', 'Takumi - Swissotel Le Concorde', 'A spirited contemporary Japanese restaurant.', 'Sashimi, Pannacotta', '', 'Takumi, meaning skilful and clever, is a spirited contemporary Japanese restaurant where the simple art of cooking holds the seeds to a deeper, more life-enriching experience.', '2 minutes’ walk from the MRT Huaykwang station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4113, 'en_US', '204 Bistro & Bar - Swissotel Le Concorde', 'A delicious culinary experience.', 'Alaska King Crab', '', 'Indulge yourself with a Chef of cultural experience in Thai, Asian, and European food. Displaying an international variety at your choice from Lasagna, BBQ Pork Rib, Smoked Salmon. Not to mention the line of traditional Thai food, Seafood Salad Bar and Tepanyaki.', '2 minutes’ walk from the MRT Huaykwang station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4314, 'en_US', 'Luna Sky Garden Café - GLOW by zinc', 'Delicious international fare meets Thai classics.', 'Pasta, Shrimp cake, Pad Thai champion', '', 'Taste the possibilities of Luna Sky Garden Café, where delicious international fare meets Thai classics. Pad Thai noodles sprinkled with lime or a juicy steak grilled to perfection. Indulge in intriguing new spices and familiar favourites.', 'Near BTS Ratchathewi Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4315, 'en_US', 'The Deck - M2 de Bangkok Hotel', 'The specialty menu consists of Thai and Western cuisine', 'Dim Sum, Pad Thai, Cocktails', '', 'Specifically designed to facilitate a lively inviting atmosphere, exhibiting chic decor surrounds and displaying an all-day dining ambiance. Choose to either chill in the comfort of our air conditioned indoors or bask and have a drink on our outdoor terrace surrounds.', 'Near MRT Sutthisan Station', '', '', '', '', '', '');